                    'slug' => 'introduction',
                    'title' => 'Introduction',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><h2 id="overview" class="wp-block-heading">Overview </h2><p>Menumium is a comprehensive cloud-based restaurant management system designed specifically for the food service industry. </p><p>Whether you operate a fine dining establishment, fast-casual restaurant, coffee house, food truck, ghost kitchen, or bakery, Menumium provides the tools you need to manage your business effectively without the complexity of multiple systems. </p><p>It helps you manage day-to-day operations like taking orders, tracking tables, handling reservations, processing payments, and analyzing performance. The goal is simple: to save you time, reduce errors, and help your business grow.</p><h2 id="who-is-menumium-for" class="wp-block-heading">Who is Menumium For?</h2><p>Menumium is designed for:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Restaurant or food business owners who want better control over their operations. </li><li>Managers looking to streamline daily tasks and improve efficiency.</li><li>Staff members who need user-friendly tools to serve customers faster.</li><li>Anyone in the food industry aiming to deliver a seamless dining experience.</li></ul><p>When you start using Menumium, you get access to:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A SaaS based restaurant management system with multi-device support.</li><li>A mobile-friendly, responsive user interface.</li><li>The freedom to manage your business from anywhere, eliminating location dependencies.</li><li>A dedicated support to help you troubleshoot issues quickly.</li></ul><p><strong>Next Steps</strong></p><p>Ready to dive deeper? The following sections of this documentation will walk you through setting up your account, using each feature, and making the most of Menumium’s capabilities.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 1,
