                100 => [
                    'id' => 101,
                    'doc_category_id' => 10,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-check-table-availability',
                    'title' => 'How to Check Table Availability',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Menumium allows you to easily check table availability, monitor reserved tables, and track on-dine (currently occupied) tables. This ensures smooth seating management across all floors.</p><h2 id="step-1-check-available-tables" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Check Available Tables</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Navigate to the <strong>Table &amp; Reservation Management</strong> section from the sidebar.</li><li>Click on <strong>Table Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="581" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/table-setup-button-navigation-0a-1024x581.webp" alt="Table Setup Button Navigation" class="wp-image-11768" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/table-setup-button-navigation-0a-1024x581.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/table-setup-button-navigation-0a-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/table-setup-button-navigation-0a-768x435.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/table-setup-button-navigation-0a-1536x871.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/table-setup-button-navigation-0a.webp 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Now, click on the <strong>Available Tables</strong> button from the left navigation.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-all-available-tables-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="View All Available Tables" class="wp-image-11806" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-all-available-tables-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-all-available-tables-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-all-available-tables-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-all-available-tables-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-all-available-tables-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A list of all currently available tables will be displayed.</li><li>To check for a specific date and time, use the <strong>date and time pickers</strong> at the top of the page and click <strong>Apply</strong>.</li></ul><h2 id="step-2-check-reserved-and-on-dine-tables" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Check Reserved and On-Dine Tables</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>Available Tables</strong> page, switch to the <strong>Reserved</strong> tab to view tables that have been booked in advance.</li><li>Select the <strong>On-dine</strong> tab to view tables that are currently occupied by customers.</li><li>Use the <strong>floor tabs</strong> (e.g., <em>1st Floor</em>, <em>2nd Floor</em>) to filter tables by their location.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/reserved-table-list-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Reserved Table List" class="wp-image-11807" style="width:1178px;height:auto" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/reserved-table-list-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/reserved-table-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/reserved-table-list-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/reserved-table-list-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/reserved-table-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>By using these options, you can easily monitor availability, reservations, and occupancy across all floors and branches in real time.</p><p><strong>Note:</strong><strong><br></strong> You can also view available tables directly from the <strong>Make Reservation</strong> tab:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Navigate to the <strong>Table &amp; Reservation Management</strong> section from the sidebar.</li><li>Click on <strong>Manage Reservation</strong>.</li><li>On the reservation page, click the <strong>Available Tables</strong> button in the top-right corner.</li><li>A list of all currently available tables will be displayed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/available-tables-from-manage-reservation-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Available Tables From Manage Reservation" class="wp-image-11808" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/available-tables-from-manage-reservation-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/available-tables-from-manage-reservation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/available-tables-from-manage-reservation-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/available-tables-from-manage-reservation-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/available-tables-from-manage-reservation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p></p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 11,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:08.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:08.000000Z',
