                121 => [
                    'id' => 122,
                    'doc_category_id' => 13,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-assign-a-new-order',
                    'title' => 'How to Assign a New Order',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to assign a new order to a deliveryman in Menumium. You can select the deliveryman from the list, choose the order ID, and assign it quickly, ensuring smooth order management and tracking.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>Dashboard</strong>, go to the sidebar on the left.</li><li>Click on <strong>User Management</strong>.</li><li>A dropdown menu will appear.</li></ul><h2 id="step-2-navigate-to-the-three-dots-menu" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Navigate to the Three Dots Menu</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the three-dots menu, click <strong>Assign New Order</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-new-order-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Assign New Order" class="wp-image-11605" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-new-order-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-new-order-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-new-order-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-new-order-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-new-order-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-assign-order" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Assign Order</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>When the form opens, it will display the deliveryman’s info. Below, choose the <strong>Order ID</strong> from the dropdown and assign the order.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-order-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Assign Order Button" class="wp-image-11606" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-order-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-order-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-order-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-order-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/assign-order-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p></p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 4,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:25.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:25.000000Z',
                ],
                122 => [
                    'id' => 123,
                    'doc_category_id' => 13,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-see-a-deliverymans-status',
                    'title' => 'How to See a Deliverymanâs Status',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to check the real-time status of your delivery personnel in Menumium. The status helps you track whether a deliveryman is available, out for delivery, or currently handling orders.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>Dashboard</strong>, go to the sidebar on the left.</li><li>Click on <strong>User Management</strong>.</li><li>A dropdown menu will appear.</li></ul><h2 id="step-2-open-delivery-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Open Delivery Management</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Delivery Management</strong>.</li><li>This will take you to the <strong>Delivery Man List</strong> page.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1024x579.webp" alt="Navigation" class="wp-image-11525" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1536x869.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d.webp 1908w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-view-the-status-column" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: View the Status Column</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Delivery Management</strong> page, you will see a table listing all registered deliverymen.</li><li>Locate the <strong>Status</strong> column in the table.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="578" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-status-0a-1024x578.webp" alt="DM Status" class="wp-image-11611" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-status-0a-1024x578.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-status-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-status-0a-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-status-0a-1536x868.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-status-0a.webp 1910w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-understand-deliveryman-status" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Understand Deliveryman Status</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The <strong>Status</strong> column shows the real-time availability of each deliveryman:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Blue toggle ON</strong> → The deliveryman is active.</li><li><strong>Toggle OFF</strong> → The deliveryman is inactive or unavailable.</li></ul></li><li>In addition, specific states may be shown, such as:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Currently Assign</strong> – The deliveryman is assigned to an order.</li><li><strong>Out for Delivery</strong> – The deliveryman is en route to deliver an order.</li><li><strong>Ongoing Order</strong> – The deliveryman is currently handling an order.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-current-order-info-0a-1024x579.webp" alt="DM Current Order Info" class="wp-image-11612" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-current-order-info-0a-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-current-order-info-0a-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-current-order-info-0a-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-current-order-info-0a-1536x869.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-current-order-info-0a.webp 1902w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p></p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 5,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:26.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:26.000000Z',
                ],
                123 => [
                    'id' => 124,
                    'doc_category_id' => 13,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-temporarily-delete-a-deliveryman',
                    'title' => 'How to Temporarily Delete a Deliveryman',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to <strong>temporarily remove a deliveryman’s profile</strong> from the active list in Menumium. The deliveryman will be moved to the <strong>Trash List</strong>, making them unavailable for new assignments while keeping their data safe for restoration later.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-delivery-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Delivery Management</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>dashboard</strong>, click on <strong>User Management</strong> in the left-hand navigation menu.</li><li>From the dropdown, select <strong>Delivery Management</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1024x579.webp" alt="Navigation" class="wp-image-11525" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1536x869.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d.webp 1908w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-open-the-delivery-man-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Open the Delivery Man List</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>Click on <strong>Delivery Man List</strong> to view all your active delivery personnel.</li><li>A table of registered deliverymen will be displayed.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="DM List" class="wp-image-11532" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-move-a-deliveryman-to-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Move a Deliveryman to Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Find the deliveryman you want to remove from the active list.</li><li>On the right-hand side of their row, click the <strong>Action (â® three-dot menu)</strong>.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="DM Move to Trash" class="wp-image-11616" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-confirm-the-action" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Confirm the Action</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li><li>Click <strong>Trash</strong> to proceed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Trash Confirmation" class="wp-image-11617" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A notification will appear at the bottom left of your screen stating:<br><em>“Delivery Man Deleted Successfully.”</em></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-1024x575.webp" alt="Success Notification" class="wp-image-11618" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h3 id="result" class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Result</strong></h3><p>The deliveryman is now moved to the <strong>Trash List</strong>. They will:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>No longer appear in the <strong>active list</strong>.</li><li>Not be eligible for <strong>new order assignments</strong>.</li><li>Still have their profile and data stored, so you can <strong>restore them later</strong> if needed.</li></ul><p>Temporarily deleting a deliveryman helps you manage availability without losing their data, ensuring flexibility to restore them whenever required.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 6,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:26.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:26.000000Z',
                ],
                124 => [
                    'id' => 125,
                    'doc_category_id' => 13,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-restore-a-delivery-man',
                    'title' => 'How to Restore a Delivery Man',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide will walk you through the process of restoring a <strong>temporarily deleted deliveryman</strong> in the Menumium dashboard. This feature is helpful if a deliveryman was mistakenly deleted and you want to reactivate their profile.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-delivery-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Delivery Management</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the left-hand navigation panel, click on <strong>User Management</strong>.</li><li>Select <strong>Delivery Management</strong> from the dropdown.</li><li>Then click on <strong>Delivery Man List</strong> to view all delivery personnel.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="DM List" class="wp-image-11532" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-access-the-trash-bin" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Access the Trash Bin</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Delivery Man List</strong> page, locate the <strong>View Trash</strong> button at the top-right corner (next to <strong>+ Add New Delivery Man</strong>).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="View Trash" class="wp-image-11619" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click on it to open the <strong>Trash List</strong>, where all deleted deliverymen are stored.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Trash List" class="wp-image-11620" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-find-and-restore-the-delivery-man" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Find and Restore the Delivery Man</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the Trash List, locate the deliveryman you wish to restore.</li><li>Click on the <strong>Restore icon</strong> next to their name.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1-1024x576.webp" alt="Restore Icon" class="wp-image-11621" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-confirmation-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Restore Confirmation" class="wp-image-11622" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-confirmation-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-confirmation-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-confirmation-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-confirmation-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-confirmation-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-confirm-restoration" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Confirm Restoration</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the pop-up, click <strong>Send Back</strong> to proceed.</li><li>A success notification will appear at the bottom of your screen confirming the restoration.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-success-notification-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Restore Success Notification" class="wp-image-11627" style="width:1178px;height:auto" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-success-notification-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-success-notification-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-success-notification-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-success-notification-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-success-notification-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-verify-restoration" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Verify Restoration</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>After confirmation, you’ll be redirected to the <strong>Delivery Man List</strong>.</li><li>The restored deliveryman will now be visible in the active list.</li><li>Refresh the page if needed to see the updated list.</li></ol><p>Restoring a deliveryman ensures you can quickly reactivate their profile and assign orders again without needing to create a new account.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 7,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:27.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:27.000000Z',
                ],
                125 => [
                    'id' => 126,
                    'doc_category_id' => 13,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-delete-a-delivery-man-permanently',
                    'title' => 'How to Delete a Delivery Man Permanently',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide provides step-by-step instructions on how to permanently delete a delivery man from the Menumium dashboard. The process involves two stages: first moving the delivery man to the <strong>Trash</strong>, and then deleting them permanently from the <strong>Trash List</strong>.</p><h2 id="step-1-move-the-delivery-man-to-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Move the Delivery Man to Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>Dashboard</strong>, go to the <strong>User Management</strong> section in the left-hand sidebar.</li><li>Under <strong>User Management</strong>, select <strong>Delivery Management</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>Delivery Man List</strong> to view all active delivery personnel.</li><li>Locate the delivery man you want to delete. In the <strong>Action</strong> column, click the <strong>three-dot menu</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-3-dots-0a-1024x573.webp" alt="DM List 3 Dots" class="wp-image-11631" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-3-dots-0a-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-3-dots-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-3-dots-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-3-dots-0a-1536x859.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-list-3-dots-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown, select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="DM Move to Trash" class="wp-image-11616" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-move-to-trash-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear. Click <strong>Trash</strong> to confirm.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Trash Confirmation" class="wp-image-11617" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success notification will appear at the bottom-left of your screen confirming that the delivery man has been moved to the trash.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-1024x575.webp" alt="Success Notification" class="wp-image-11618" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-permanently-delete-from-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Permanently Delete from Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Go back to the <strong>Delivery Management</strong> menu in the sidebar and select <strong>Delivery Man Trash List</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Trash List" class="wp-image-11620" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The page will display all delivery men who have been moved to the trash.</li><li>Find the delivery man you want to delete permanently.</li><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column, click the <strong>red bin icon</strong> next to their name.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0f-1024x576.webp" alt="Delete Icon" class="wp-image-11636" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0f-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0f-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0f-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0f-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0f.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear. Click <strong>Delete</strong> to finalize the action.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x577.webp" alt="Delete Confirmation Popup" class="wp-image-11632" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-popup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-popup-0a-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-popup-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-popup-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A final notification will confirm that the delivery man has been <strong>permanently deleted</strong> from the system.</li></ul><p>By following these steps, you can safely remove a delivery man’s profile from your system. Once permanently deleted, their data cannot be recovered.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 8,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:28.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:28.000000Z',
                ],
                126 => [
                    'id' => 127,
                    'doc_category_id' => 13,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-monitor-the-delivery-management-dashboard',
                    'title' => 'How to Monitor the Delivery Management Dashboard',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>The Delivery Management Dashboard provides a centralized view of all delivery-related operations. It is divided into two main sections: <strong>Order Statistics</strong> and <strong>Deliveryman Statistics</strong>.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-delivery-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Delivery Management</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From your Menumium dashboard, go to the left-side navigation panel.</li><li>Click on <strong>User Management &gt; Delivery Management.</strong></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1024x579.webp" alt="Navigation" class="wp-image-11525" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d-1536x869.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigation-0d.webp 1908w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-access-the-dashboard" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Access the Dashboard</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Dashboard</strong>.</li><li>This will open the main Delivery Management Dashboard.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="DM Dashboard" class="wp-image-11633" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-review-order-statistics" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Review Order Statistics</h2><p>The <strong>Order Statistics</strong> section shows real-time updates on order statuses:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Total Ongoing Orders</strong> – Number of orders currently in progress.</li><li><strong>Total Assigned Orders</strong> – Number of orders that have already been assigned to a delivery person.</li><li><strong>Total Delivered Orders</strong> – Number of orders successfully completed and delivered.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-order-stat-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="DM Dashboard Order Stat" class="wp-image-11634" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-order-stat-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-order-stat-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-order-stat-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-order-stat-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dm-dashboard-order-stat-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-review-deliveryman-statistics" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Review Deliveryman Statistics</h2><p>The <strong>Deliveryman Statistics</strong> section gives insights into your team’s availability:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Total Active Deliveryman</strong> – Number of delivery personnel currently logged in and active.</li><li><strong>Engaged Deliveryman</strong> – Number of delivery personnel currently handling an active order.</li><li><strong>Free Deliveryman</strong> – Number of delivery personnel available to take new orders.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dashboard-dm-stat-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Dashboard DM Stat" class="wp-image-11635" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dashboard-dm-stat-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dashboard-dm-stat-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dashboard-dm-stat-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dashboard-dm-stat-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dashboard-dm-stat-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>Using this dashboard, you can quickly assess delivery performance, team workload, and order flow in real-time.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 9,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:28.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:28.000000Z',
                ],
                127 => [
                    'id' => 128,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-create-a-customer-profile-in-menumium',
                    'title' => 'How to Create a Customer Profile in Menumium',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Creating customer profiles in <strong>Menumium</strong> helps you maintain records of your regular customers, including their contact details and addresses. This makes it easier to manage orders, reservations, and customer relationships.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Customer Setup</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>Dashboard</strong>, open the left-hand sidebar.</li><li>Under the <strong>User Management</strong> section, click on <strong>Customer Setup</strong>.</li><li>This will take you to the <strong>Customer List</strong> page.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Navigate To Customer Setup" class="wp-image-10870" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-add-a-new-customer" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Add a New Customer</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Customer List</strong> page, click the green <strong>+ Add New Customer</strong> button in the top-right corner.</li><li>A pop-up window will appear for adding customer details.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/add-new-customer-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Add New Customer" class="wp-image-10872" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/add-new-customer-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/add-new-customer-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/add-new-customer-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/add-new-customer-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/add-new-customer-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-enter-customer-information" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Enter Customer Information</h2><p>Fill in the customer’s details in the form:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Name</strong> – Enter the full name of the customer.</li><li><strong>Phone</strong> – Provide the customer’s phone number.</li><li><strong>Email</strong> – Enter the customer’s email address.</li><li><strong>Customer Image</strong> – Upload an image by clicking <strong>Browse</strong> or drag and drop a file (formats supported: JPG, PNG, JPEG, WEBP).</li><li><strong>Address</strong> – To add an address, click <strong>+ Add Address</strong> and fill in the fields.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="581" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/enter-customer-information-1024x581.webp" alt="Enter Customer Information" class="wp-image-10867" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/enter-customer-information-1024x581.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/enter-customer-information-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/enter-customer-information-768x435.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/enter-customer-information-1536x871.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/enter-customer-information.webp 1903w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-save-the-profile" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Save the Profile</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After entering all the details, click the <strong>Save</strong> button at the bottom of the window.</li><li>A confirmation message will appear.</li><li>The new customer profile will now be listed in the <strong>Customer List</strong>.</li></ul></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 1,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:29.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:29.000000Z',
                ],
                128 => [
                    'id' => 129,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-update-customer-details',
                    'title' => 'How to Update Customer Details',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide walks you through the process of updating a customer’s information in the Menumium dashboard. Use this feature to correct or modify a customer’s <strong>name, phone number, email, or profile image</strong>.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><p>From the Menumium dashboard, go to the left-hand sidebar and click on <strong>User Management</strong> to expand the menu.</p><h2 id="step-2-select-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Select Customer Setup</h2><p>Within the expanded menu, click on <strong>Customer Setup</strong>. This will open the <strong>Customer List</strong> page, showing all registered customers.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Navigate To Customer Setup" class="wp-image-10870" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-find-the-customer-to-update" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Find the Customer to Update</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Customer List page, locate the customer you want to update.</li><li>Use the <strong>Search bar</strong> at the top of the page to quickly find them by name, phone number, or email.</li></ol><h2 id="step-4-open-the-edit-customer-details-window" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Open the Edit Customer Details Window</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column of the customer’s row, click on the <strong>three-dot icon (â®)</strong>.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Edit Customer</strong>.</li><li>A pop-up window titled <strong>Edit Customer</strong> will appear.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/search-and-edit-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Search &amp; Edit" class="wp-image-10875" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/search-and-edit-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/search-and-edit-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/search-and-edit-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/search-and-edit-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/search-and-edit-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-update-the-information" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Update the Information</h2><p>In the <strong>Edit Customer</strong> window, you can update the following details:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Name</strong> – Update or correct the customer’s full name.</li><li><strong>Phone</strong> – Edit the customer’s contact number.</li><li><strong>Email</strong> – Update their email address.</li><li><strong>Image</strong> – Upload or replace the customer’s profile image.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-customer-info-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Update Customer Info" class="wp-image-10877" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-customer-info-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-customer-info-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-customer-info-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-customer-info-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-customer-info-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-save-the-changes" class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Step 6: Save the Changes</strong></h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After making the necessary updates, click the <strong>Update</strong> button at the bottom of the pop-up window.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-10879" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation message will appear, indicating that the customer’s details were successfully updated.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-message-customer-update-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Confirmation Message Customer Update" class="wp-image-10928" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-message-customer-update-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-message-customer-update-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-message-customer-update-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-message-customer-update-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-message-customer-update-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>Your customer’s information is now up to date in the system.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Update &amp; Save" class="wp-image-10879" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-and-save-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 2,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:30.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:30.000000Z',
                ],
                129 => [
                    'id' => 130,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-see-customer-details-in-menumium',
                    'title' => 'How to See Customer Details in Menumium',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Menumium allows you to access detailed customer profiles directly from the dashboard. This feature is helpful for managing customer relationships, viewing order history, and tracking their overall interactions with your restaurant.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Customer Setup</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>Dashboard</strong>, open the left-hand sidebar.</li><li>Click on <strong>User Management</strong>.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Customer Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Navigate To Customer Setup" class="wp-image-10870" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-view-the-customer-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: View the Customer List</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The <strong>Customer List</strong> page will display all registered customers.</li><li>This list provides key details at a glance, including:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Customer Name</strong></li><li><strong>Contact Information</strong> (phone and email)</li><li><strong>Total Orders</strong></li><li><strong>Joining Date</strong></li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-list-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="View Customer List" class="wp-image-10884" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-list-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-list-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-list-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-access-customer-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Access Customer Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Find the customer you want to view.</li><li>On the right side of their row, click the <strong>three-dot menu (â®)</strong> in the <strong>Action</strong> column.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>View Details</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="View Customer Details" class="wp-image-10886" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-review-customer-profile" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Review Customer Profile</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>You will be redirected to a detailed customer profile page.</li><li>This page provides a comprehensive overview, including:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Profile Information</strong> (name, contact info, and profile image)</li><li><strong>Order Analytics </strong>(Completion rate, ongoing rate, canceled, refunded, return rate failed rate)</li><li><strong>Order History</strong></li><li><strong>Coupon History </strong>(availed coupon details)</li><li><strong>Summary of Interactions</strong> with your restaurant.</li><li><strong>Profile Analytics </strong>(Total Order, Total Reservation)</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/review-customer-profile-0a-1024x579.webp" alt="Review Customer Profile" class="wp-image-10887" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/review-customer-profile-0a-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/review-customer-profile-0a-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/review-customer-profile-0a-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/review-customer-profile-0a-1536x869.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/review-customer-profile-0a.webp 1908w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>By following these steps, you can quickly view and analyze customer details in Menumium. This makes it easier to understand customer behavior, personalize their experience, and build stronger relationships with your customer base.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 3,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:31.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:31.000000Z',
                ],
                130 => [
                    'id' => 131,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-block-and-unblock-customers',
                    'title' => 'How to Block and Unblock Customers',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to manage customer access to your digital menu and services by blocking or unblocking them from the Menumium dashboard.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><p>From the Menumium dashboard, click on <strong>User Management</strong> in the left-hand navigation menu to manage all user accounts.</p><h2 id="step-2-go-to-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Go to Customer Setup</h2><p>Under the <strong>User Management</strong> submenu, select <strong>Customer Setup</strong> to view a list of all your registered customers.</p><h2 id="step-3-block-a-customer" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Block a Customer</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>On the customer list page, find the customer you want to block.</li><li>In the <strong>Unblock/Block</strong> column, click the toggle button.</li><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear. Click <strong>Block</strong> to confirm.</li><li>A success notification will confirm that the customer’s status has been updated.</li></ol><p>Once blocked, the customer will not be able to view your digital menu or place orders.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/block-or-unblock-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Block Or Unblock" class="wp-image-10890" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/block-or-unblock-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/block-or-unblock-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/block-or-unblock-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/block-or-unblock-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/block-or-unblock-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-unblock-a-customer" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Unblock a Customer</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>To unblock a customer, find them in the list and click the toggle button in the <strong>Unblock/Block</strong> column.</li><li>A success notification will confirm the update.</li></ol><p>Once unblocked, the customer regains access to your digital menu and services.</p><p>Blocking and unblocking customers in Menumium is a quick way to control access and manage user activity, helping you maintain a secure and efficient customer experience.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 4,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:32.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:32.000000Z',
                ],
                131 => [
                    'id' => 132,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-check-customer-order-analytics-or-history',
                    'title' => 'How to Check Customer Order Analytics or History',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to view a customer’s order analytics and history in Menumium. By following these steps, you can access detailed insights into customer behavior, including completion, ongoing, and cancellation rates, as well as their full order history.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><p>From the dashboard, locate and click on the <strong>User Management</strong> icon in the left-hand sidebar. This will open the User Management submenu.</p><h2 id="step-2-go-to-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Go to Customer Setup</h2><p>Click on <strong>Customer Setup</strong> under the User Management submenu. You will be taken to the <strong>Customer List</strong> page, where all registered customers are displayed.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Navigate To Customer Setup" class="wp-image-10870" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-open-customer-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Open Customer Details</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Customer List</strong> page, find the customer whose information you want to view.</li><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column (three-dot menu), click to expand the options.</li><li>Select <strong>View Details</strong> from the dropdown.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="View Customer Details" class="wp-image-10886" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-customer-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-view-order-analytics" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: View Order Analytics</h2><p>On the <strong>Customer Details</strong> page, you will see the <strong>Order Analytics</strong> section. This area displays key performance metrics such as:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Completion Rate</strong> – Percentage of orders successfully completed.</li><li><strong>Ongoing Rate</strong> – Percentage of orders still in progress.</li><li><strong>Cancellation Rate</strong> – Percentage of orders canceled.</li><li><strong>Refund Rate</strong> – Percentage of orders refunded.</li><li><strong>Return Rate</strong> – Percentage of orders returned.</li><li><strong>Failed Rate</strong> – Percentage of orders failed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-analytics-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Order Analytics" class="wp-image-10893" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-analytics-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-analytics-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-analytics-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-analytics-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-analytics-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-review-order-history" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Review Order History</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>Scroll down to the <strong>Order History</strong> tab.</li><li>This section contains a full list of the customer’s past orders.</li><li>Each record shows details such as order ID, date, status, and order total.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="583" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-history-0a-1024x583.webp" alt="Order History" class="wp-image-10894" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-history-0a-1024x583.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-history-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-history-0a-768x437.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-history-0a-1536x875.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/order-history-0a.webp 1895w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-view-customer-coupon-history" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: View Customer Coupon History</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Beside the <strong>Order History</strong> click the <strong>Coupon</strong> tab.</li><li>Use the search bar to find coupons by code or keyword.</li><li>Check details such as coupon code, type, discount amount, usage limit, expiry date, and status (availed or not availed).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-history-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Coupon History
" class="wp-image-10896" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-history-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-history-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-history-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-history-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-history-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Review the number of times each coupon has been used under the Usage column.</li><li>Click the eye icon under the Action column to view full coupon details.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-eye-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Coupon Eye Button" class="wp-image-10897" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-eye-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-eye-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-eye-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-eye-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-eye-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="580" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-details-0a-1024x580.webp" alt="Coupon Details" class="wp-image-10898" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-details-0a-1024x580.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-details-0a-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-details-0a-768x435.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-details-0a-1536x870.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/coupon-details-0a.webp 1906w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Use Filter to refine results or Export to download the coupon list.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="584" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-and-export-0a-1024x584.webp" alt="Filter &amp; Export" class="wp-image-10899" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-and-export-0a-1024x584.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-and-export-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-and-export-0a-768x438.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-and-export-0a-1536x876.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-and-export-0a.webp 1892w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>By checking customer order analytics and history, you gain valuable insights into their behavior and preferences, helping you improve service quality and customer retention.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 5,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:33.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:33.000000Z',
                ],
                132 => [
                    'id' => 133,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-create-a-coupon-for-a-specific-customer',
                    'title' => 'How to Create a Coupon for a Specific Customer',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Creating a coupon for a specific customer allows you to offer special promotions, discounts, or loyalty rewards. Follow these steps in the Menumium dashboard to create one.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-customer-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Customer Management</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From the left-hand navigation menu, click on <strong>User Management</strong>.</li><li>Select <strong>Customer Setup</strong> to open the customer list.</li></ol><h2 id="step-2-find-the-customer" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Find the Customer</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Customer List</strong> page, locate the customer you want to create a coupon for.</li><li>Use the <strong>search bar</strong> or scroll through the list to find them.</li><li>Once found, click the <strong>three-dot icon (â®)</strong> on the right side of their row.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="3 Dot Icon" class="wp-image-10902" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a.webp 1914w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-create-the-coupon" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Create the Coupon</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Create Coupon</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Coupon" class="wp-image-10903" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A <strong>Create Coupon</strong> window will appear. Fill in the required details:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Coupon Title:</strong> Enter a descriptive name (e.g., <em>“Loyalty Reward”</em> or <em>“First-Time Discount”</em>).</li><li><strong>Coupon Code:</strong> A code is generated automatically. Click <strong>Generate Code</strong> to create a new one if needed.</li><li><strong>Maximum Number of Times:</strong> Enter how many times this coupon can be applied (e.g., <em>1 for one-time use</em>). Or, check <strong>Unlimited Usage</strong>.</li><li><strong>Discount Type:</strong> Choose from options such as <em>Discount on Purchase</em>, <em>First Order</em>, <em>Free Item with Purchase</em>, or <em>Free Delivery</em>.</li><li><strong>Discount Amount:</strong> Enter the discount value (e.g., <em>10</em> for 10%).</li><li><strong>Max. Amount:</strong> Set a maximum limit to prevent overly large deductions.</li><li><strong>Validity:</strong> Select a start and end date. Or, check <strong>Assign this offer permanently</strong> for no expiry.</li><li><strong>Order Type:</strong> Specify where the coupon applies (e.g., <em>Dine-In</em>, <em>Take Away</em>, <em>Home Delivery</em>).</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0b-1024x574.webp" alt="Create Coupon" class="wp-image-10904" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0b-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0b-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0b-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0b-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-0b.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After filling in all fields, click <strong>Create</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-2-1024x575.webp" alt="Create Coupon 2" class="wp-image-9251" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-2-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-2-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-2-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-2-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-coupon-2.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-confirmation" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Confirmation</h2><p>A success message — <em>“Coupon Successfully Added”</em> — will appear at the bottom of the screen. The new coupon will now be listed under the <strong>Coupon</strong> section in your dashboard, ready for use.</p><p>By creating customer-specific coupons, you can strengthen loyalty and reward regulars with exclusive offers tailored just for them.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 6,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:33.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:33.000000Z',
                ],
                133 => [
                    'id' => 134,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-delete-a-customer-temporarily-in-menumium',
                    'title' => 'How to Delete a Customer Temporarily in Menumium',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Deleting a customer temporarily in Menumium moves their profile to the <strong>Trash</strong>. This means the customer’s data becomes inactive, but you can restore it later if needed.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>Menumium dashboard</strong>, go to the <strong>left-hand sidebar</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>User Management</strong> to expand the submenu.</li></ol><h2 id="step-2-open-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Open Customer Setup</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>In the submenu, click on <strong>Customer Setup</strong>.</li><li>This will take you to the <strong>Customer List</strong> page, showing all active customers.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Navigate To Customer Setup" class="wp-image-10870" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-locate-the-customer" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Locate the Customer</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Customer List page, search for the customer you want to delete.</li><li>Use the <strong>search bar</strong> at the top to find them by <strong>name, phone number, or email</strong>.</li></ol><h2 id="step-4-access-more-options" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Access More Options</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>Once you’ve located the customer, look at the <strong>Action column</strong> on the right-hand side.</li><li>Click on the <strong>three-dot menu (â®)</strong> to open additional options.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="3 Dot Icon" class="wp-image-10902" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/three-dot-icon-0a.webp 1914w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-move-customer-to-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Move Customer to Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="571" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1024x571.webp" alt="Move To Trash" class="wp-image-10908" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A <strong>confirmation pop-up</strong> will appear, reminding you that the customer will become inactive but can be restored later.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-pop-up-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Trash Confirmation Pop Up" class="wp-image-10925" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-pop-up-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-pop-up-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-pop-up-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-pop-up-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-pop-up-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-confirm-deletion" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Confirm Deletion</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click the <strong>Trash</strong> button in the confirmation pop-up to proceed.</li><li>A success notification, <strong>“Customer Successfully Deleted,”</strong> will appear at the bottom of your screen.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Confirm Deletion" class="wp-image-10912" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>The customer is now inactive and will no longer appear in your active list, but can still be restored from the Trash section.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 7,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:34.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:34.000000Z',
                ],
                134 => [
                    'id' => 135,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-restore-a-temporarily-deleted-customer',
                    'title' => 'How to Restore a Temporarily Deleted Customer',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>If a customer has been moved to the <strong>Trash</strong>, you can easily restore them to your active customer list. This is useful when a customer was deleted by mistake or if you want to reinstate their access and records.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From your <strong>Menumium dashboard</strong>, go to the <strong>left-hand menu</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>User Management</strong> to expand the submenu.</li></ol><h2 id="step-2-open-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Open Customer Setup</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From the expanded submenu, select <strong>Customer Setup</strong>.</li><li>This will take you to the <strong>Customer List</strong> page.</li></ol><h2 id="step-3-access-the-trash-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Access the Trash List</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Customer List page, locate the <strong>View Trash</strong> button (top-right).</li><li>Click on it to see all customers who have been temporarily deleted.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="View Trash" class="wp-image-10917" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-restore-a-customer" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Restore a Customer</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the <strong>Customer Trash List</strong>, find the customer you wish to restore.</li><li>Click the <strong>Restore icon</strong> next to their name.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Restore Icon" class="wp-image-10919" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-restoration-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Confirm Restoration" class="wp-image-10920" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-restoration-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-restoration-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-restoration-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-restoration-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-restoration-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-confirm-the-restoration" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Confirm the Restoration</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the confirmation pop-up, click <strong>Send Back</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Send Back" class="wp-image-10922" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success notification, <strong>“Customer Successfully Restored,”</strong> will appear at the bottom of your screen.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/successfully-restored-0a-1024x573.webp" alt="Successfully Restored" class="wp-image-10923" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/successfully-restored-0a-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/successfully-restored-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/successfully-restored-0a-768x429.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/successfully-restored-0a-1536x859.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/successfully-restored-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The customer’s profile will now reappear in the active <strong>Customer List</strong>.</li></ul><p>The restored customer regains full access to your digital menu and services.</p><p></p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 8,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:35.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:35.000000Z',
                ],
                135 => [
                    'id' => 136,
                    'doc_category_id' => 14,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-delete-a-customer-permanently',
                    'title' => 'How to Delete a Customer Permanently',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to <strong>permanently remove a customer</strong> from your Menumium system.</p><div class="wp-block-group doc-warning"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong>Warning</strong></p><p>This action is <strong>irreversible</strong> — once deleted, the customer’s data is removed from the database and cannot be recovered.</p></div></div><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-user-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to User Management</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From your <strong>Menumium dashboard</strong>, click on <strong>User Management</strong> in the left-hand sidebar.</li><li>This section allows you to manage all customer and user-related data.</li></ol><h2 id="step-2-access-customer-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Access Customer Setup</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>Within the <strong>User Management</strong> submenu, select <strong>Customer Setup</strong>.</li><li>The <strong>Customer List</strong> page will open, displaying all registered customers.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Navigate To Customer Setup" class="wp-image-10870" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-customer-setup-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-move-the-customer-to-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Move the Customer to Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the customer you wish to delete.</li><li>On the right side of their entry, click the <strong>three-dot action icon (â®)</strong>.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="571" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1024x571.webp" alt="Move To Trash" class="wp-image-10908" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A notification will confirm that the customer has been moved to Trash.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Confirm Deletion" class="wp-image-10912" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-open-the-trash-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Open the Trash List</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Customer List page, click the <strong>View Trash</strong> button (top-right).</li><li>This will display the <strong>Customer Trash List</strong>, showing all temporarily deleted customers.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customer-trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Customer Trash List" class="wp-image-10931" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customer-trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customer-trash-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customer-trash-list-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customer-trash-list-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customer-trash-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-permanently-delete-the-customer" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Permanently Delete the Customer</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the Trash List, locate the customer you want to permanently remove.</li><li>Click the <strong>red trash can icon</strong> next to their name.</li><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear, warning that this action is <strong>permanent</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Delete</strong> to finalize.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/permanently-delete-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Permanently Delete" class="wp-image-10932" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/permanently-delete-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/permanently-delete-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/permanently-delete-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/permanently-delete-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/permanently-delete-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>The customer’s profile and all related data will now be <strong>permanently deleted</strong> from your Menumium system.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 9,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:35.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:35.000000Z',
                ],
                136 => [
                    'id' => 137,
                    'doc_category_id' => 15,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-add-a-new-supplier-in-menumium',
                    'title' => 'How to Add a New Supplier in Menumium',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Adding suppliers in Menumium helps you organize vendor details for better inventory and purchase management. Follow these steps to add a new supplier profile.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-supplier-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Supplier Setup</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dashboard, go to the <strong>Inventory &amp; Recipe Management</strong> section.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Inventory Nav" class="wp-image-11473" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>Click on <strong>Supplier Setup</strong> to open the supplier list.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Supplier Nav" class="wp-image-11474" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-create-a-new-supplier" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Create a New Supplier</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>You will find two buttons for new supplier creation on the <strong>Supplier List</strong> page, click the <strong>+ Create New Supplier</strong> button in the top-right corner.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-supplier-button-0a-1024x573.webp" alt="Create Supplier Button" class="wp-image-11475" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-supplier-button-0a-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-supplier-button-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-supplier-button-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-supplier-button-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-supplier-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A <strong>Create Supplier</strong> pop-up window will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-window-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create New Supplier Window" class="wp-image-11476" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-window-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-window-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-window-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-window-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-window-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-fill-in-supplier-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Fill in Supplier Details</h2><p>Provide the required information under the form fields:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Contact Person Name:</strong> Enter the name of your contact at the supplier company.</li><li><strong>Phone Number:</strong> Add the primary contact number.</li><li><strong>Email:</strong> Enter the supplier’s email address.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-details-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create New Supplier Details" class="wp-image-11477" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-details-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-details-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-details-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-supplier-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-expand-for-more-details-optional" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Expand for More Details (Optional)</h2><p>Click <strong>+ See More</strong> to add detailed company information.</p><p><strong>Company Info</strong></p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Company Name:</strong> Legal name of the supplier’s company.</li><li><strong>Phone Number:</strong> Main company contact number.</li><li><strong>Email:</strong> Company’s general email.</li><li><strong>Address:</strong> Physical business address.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-info-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Company Info" class="wp-image-11478" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-info-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-info-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-info-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-info-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-info-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p><strong>Company Logo</strong></p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Upload the supplier’s logo for easy identification (<em>PNG, JPG, JPEG, WEBP supported</em>).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Company Logo" class="wp-image-11479" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p><strong>Additional Documents</strong></p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Upload contracts, agreements, or other relevant documents  (<em>PNG, JPG, JPEG, WEBP supported</em>) if needed.</li></ul><h2 id="step-5-save-the-supplier" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Save the Supplier</h2><p>Once all the details are filled in, click the green <strong>Create</strong> button at the bottom of the form.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/additional-doc-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Additional Doc" class="wp-image-11480" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/additional-doc-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/additional-doc-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/additional-doc-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/additional-doc-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/additional-doc-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-confirmation" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Confirmation</h2><p>A success message — <em>“Supplier created successfully”</em> — will appear in the bottom-left corner. The new supplier will now be visible in your <strong>Supplier List</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Supplier List" class="wp-image-11481" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>By adding suppliers in Menumium, you ensure smooth purchase tracking and maintain organized records of vendor relationships.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 1,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:36.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:36.000000Z',
                ],
                137 => [
                    'id' => 138,
                    'doc_category_id' => 15,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-edit-supplier-details-in-menumium',
                    'title' => 'How to Edit Supplier Details in Menumium',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to manage your existing suppliers by updating their details, changing their status, or deleting them from your Menumium account.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-supplier-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Supplier Setup</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the left-hand navigation menu, go to <strong>Inventory &amp; Recipe Management</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>Supplier Setup</strong> to open the Supplier List page.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Inventory Nav" class="wp-image-11473" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Supplier Nav" class="wp-image-11474" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-locate-the-supplier" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Locate the Supplier</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Supplier List</strong> page, find the supplier you want to edit.</li><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column on the right-hand side, click the <strong>three-dot menu (â®)</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/action-3-dots-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Action 3 Dots" class="wp-image-11482" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/action-3-dots-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/action-3-dots-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/action-3-dots-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/action-3-dots-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/action-3-dots-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-choose-an-action" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Choose an Action</h2><p>The dropdown menu provides the following options:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Status Toggle:</strong> Activate or deactivate the supplier.<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><em>On:</em> Supplier is active and available.</li><li><em>Off:</em> Supplier is hidden from the active supplier list.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-status-toggle-0a-1024x573.webp" alt="Supplier Status Toggle" class="wp-image-11483" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-status-toggle-0a-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-status-toggle-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-status-toggle-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-status-toggle-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-status-toggle-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Edit Details:</strong> Opens a pop-up window where you can update the supplier’s information.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Details Button" class="wp-image-11497" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>View Purchase History: </strong>Opens the Purchase List page showing Purchase ID, Date, Total Purchase, Total Amount, and an Action column.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="567" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-purchase-history-button-0a-1024x567.webp" alt="View Purchase History Button" class="wp-image-11484" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-purchase-history-button-0a-1024x567.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-purchase-history-button-0a-300x166.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-purchase-history-button-0a-768x426.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-purchase-history-button-0a-1536x851.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-purchase-history-button-0a.webp 1924w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/purchase-history-page-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Purchase History Page" class="wp-image-11485" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/purchase-history-page-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/purchase-history-page-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/purchase-history-page-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/purchase-history-page-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/purchase-history-page-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Move to Trash:</strong> Deletes the supplier and moves them to the trash list.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Move to Trash Button" class="wp-image-11486" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-edit-supplier-information" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Edit Supplier Information</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Edit Details</strong> from the dropdown.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Details Button" class="wp-image-11497" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the pop-up window, update any supplier information such as:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Contact Person Name</li><li>Phone Number</li><li>Email</li><li>Company Info (name, address, email, phone)</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="571" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-supplier-info-0a-1024x571.webp" alt="Update Supplier Info" class="wp-image-11488" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-supplier-info-0a-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-supplier-info-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-supplier-info-0a-768x429.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-supplier-info-0a-1536x857.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-supplier-info-0a.webp 1921w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Company Logo or Supporting Documents</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-and-additional-doc-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Company Logo &amp; Additional Doc" class="wp-image-11489" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-and-additional-doc-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-and-additional-doc-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-and-additional-doc-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-and-additional-doc-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/company-logo-and-additional-doc-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Once done, click <strong>Update</strong> to save changes.</li></ul><h2 id="step-5-delete-a-supplier-optional" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Delete a Supplier (Optional)</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Move to Trash</strong> from the dropdown.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Move to Trash Button" class="wp-image-11486" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Move to Trash Confirmation Popup" class="wp-image-11491" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Move to Trash</strong> to confirm. A success notification will pop up.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Delete Success Noti" class="wp-image-11492" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>By editing supplier details in Menumium, you can keep vendor information accurate, ensure smooth purchase operations, and maintain a clean and updated supplier list.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 2,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:37.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:37.000000Z',
