                138 => [
                    'id' => 139,
                    'doc_category_id' => 15,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-manage-and-view-supplier-details-in-menumium',
                    'title' => 'How to Manage and View Supplier Details in Menumium',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide will show you how to view supplier details and manage their status or records within the Menumium system.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-supplier-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Supplier Setup</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Inventory &amp; Recipe Management</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>Supplier Setup</strong> to open the Supplier List page.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Inventory Nav" class="wp-image-11473" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Supplier Nav" class="wp-image-11474" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-locate-the-supplier" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Locate the Supplier</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Supplier List</strong> page, find the supplier you want to manage.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Supplier List" class="wp-image-11481" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column on the right side, click the <strong>eye icon</strong> to view more options.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-supplier-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Eye Icon Supplier" class="wp-image-11502" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-supplier-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-supplier-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-supplier-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-supplier-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-supplier-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Clicking the <strong>eye icon</strong> opens a supplier quick view showing status toggle, delete option, joining date, total purchases, total amount, number of purchases, company details, and contact person info.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Eye Icon Details" class="wp-image-11503" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="Eye Icon Details" class="wp-image-11504" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/eye-icon-details-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-view-supplier-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: View Supplier Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Clicking <strong>View Details </strong>at the bottom will open a dedicated page for the selected supplier.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="View Details Button" class="wp-image-11517" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>This page displays:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Contact Person Information</li><li>Phone Number and Email</li><li>Company Information (Name, Address, Email, Phone)</li><li>Purchase History related to this supplier</li><li>It also displays a <strong>Purchase List</strong> with Purchase ID, Date, Total Purchase, Total Amount, and an Action column.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-page-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="View Details Page" class="wp-image-11505" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-page-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-page-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-page-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-page-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-page-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-manage-supplier-options" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Manage Supplier Options</h2><p>You can also perform the following action upon clicking on “View Details”:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Edit Supplier:</strong> Opens a pop-up window to update supplier information such as contact details, company info, or uploaded documents.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-edit-supplier-0c-1024x574.webp" alt="View Details, Edit Supplier" class="wp-image-11507" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-edit-supplier-0c-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-edit-supplier-0c-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-edit-supplier-0c-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-edit-supplier-0c-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-edit-supplier-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Delete Supplier:</strong> Permanently removes the supplier from your list. A confirmation pop-up will appear before deletion.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-delete-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="View Details, Delete" class="wp-image-11508" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-delete-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-delete-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-delete-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-delete-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-delete-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Status Toggle:</strong> Quickly activate or deactivate the supplier.<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><em>Active:</em> Supplier remains visible and usable.</li><li><em>Inactive:</em> Supplier will be hidden from the active supplier list.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-status-toggle-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="View Details, Status Toggle" class="wp-image-11509" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-status-toggle-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-status-toggle-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-status-toggle-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-status-toggle-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-status-toggle-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>Menumium makes supplier management simple by giving you quick access to their details, purchase history, and account status, ensuring smooth vendor relationships and accurate records.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 3,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:38.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:38.000000Z',
                ],
                139 => [
                    'id' => 140,
                    'doc_category_id' => 15,
                    'slug' => 'how-to-delete-suppliers-in-menumium',
                    'title' => 'How to Delete Suppliers in Menumium',
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide will walk you through the process of deleting a supplier, restoring a deleted supplier, or permanently removing them from your Menumium account.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-supplier-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Supplier Setup</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Inventory &amp; Recipe Management</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>Supplier Setup</strong> to open the Supplier List page.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Inventory Nav" class="wp-image-11473" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/inventory-nav-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Supplier Nav" class="wp-image-11474" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-nav-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-move-a-supplier-to-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Move a Supplier to Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the Supplier List, locate the supplier you want to delete.</li><li>Click the <strong>three dots (â®) menu</strong> in the <strong>Action</strong> column.</li><li>Select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Move to Trash Button" class="wp-image-11486" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear. Click <strong>Move to Trash</strong> again to confirm.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Move to Trash Confirmation Popup" class="wp-image-11491" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-confirmation-popup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success notification will appear at the bottom of the screen.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Delete Success Noti" class="wp-image-11492" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-success-notification-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-access-the-trash-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Access the Trash List</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Supplier List page, click the <strong>View Trash</strong> button (top-right corner).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-1024x575.webp" alt="View Trash Button" class="wp-image-11510" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>This will open the <strong>Supplier Trash List</strong>, where all deleted suppliers are temporarily stored.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Supplier Trash List" class="wp-image-11511" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-restore-or-permanently-delete-a-supplier" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Restore or Permanently Delete a Supplier</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>To Restore a Supplier:</strong><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Find the supplier you want to bring back.</li><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column, click the <strong>Restore icon</strong> (circular arrow).</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Restore Icon" class="wp-image-11512" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear. Click <strong>Send Back</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-confirmation-popup-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="Send Back Confirmation Popup" class="wp-image-11513" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-confirmation-popup-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-confirmation-popup-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-confirmation-popup-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-confirmation-popup-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-confirmation-popup-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The supplier will return to your active list.</li></ul><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>To Permanently Delete a Supplier:</strong><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Go to View Trash and open Supplier Trash List.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-1024x575.webp" alt="View Trash Button" class="wp-image-11510" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Supplier Trash List" class="wp-image-11511" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/supplier-trash-list-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Find the supplier you want to remove permanently.</li><li>Click the Delete icon.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Delete Icon" class="wp-image-11514" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li><li>Click Delete. The supplier will be permanently deleted, and this action cannot be undone.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Delete Confirmation" class="wp-image-11515" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>Menumium allows you to manage supplier records flexibly. You can temporarily delete and restore suppliers when needed, or permanently remove them if they are no longer relevant.</p></div>',
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'order' => 4,
                    'status' => 'published',
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:54:38.000000Z',
