                23 => [
                    'id' => 24,
                    'doc_page_id' => 179,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Updating a food item allows you to change its details, pricing, or linked attributes in Menumium.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/6-5-1024x576.webp" alt="Update a Food Item" class="wp-image-9536" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/6-5-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/6-5-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/6-5-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/6-5-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/6-5.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-the-food-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to the Food List</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>dashboard</strong>, go to the left-hand sidebar.</li><li>Click Menu <strong>Setup Management &gt; Food Management &gt; Food Setup.</strong></li><li>This will display a list of all your current food items.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="585" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/access-category-setup-0a-1024x585.webp" alt="Access Category Setup" class="wp-image-11140" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/access-category-setup-0a-1024x585.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/access-category-setup-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/access-category-setup-0a-768x439.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/access-category-setup-0a-1536x877.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/access-category-setup-0a.webp 1888w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-select-the-item-to-update" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Select the Item to Update</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Food List</strong> screen, locate the item you want to edit.</li><li>Click the <strong>three-dot menu</strong> icon on the right side of the item’s row.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Edit Details</strong>.</li><li>A new window will open, allowing you to modify the food item.</li></ul><h2 id="step-3-update-item-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Update Item Details</h2><p>The edit screen contains multiple tabs for updating information:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Basic</strong> – Edit name, description, image, availability, etc.</li><li><strong>Variation &amp; Price</strong> – Adjust variations, sizes, or prices.</li><li><strong>Add-ons</strong> – Manage optional extras linked to this food.</li><li><strong>Labels</strong> – Apply labels such as “Organic,” “Spicy,” etc.</li><li><strong>Cuisine Setup</strong> – Link the food to a specific cuisine.</li><li><strong>Recipe &amp; Ingredients</strong> – Assign or update the recipe and ingredient details.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="583" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-item-details-0a-1024x583.webp" alt="Update Item Details" class="wp-image-11187" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-item-details-0a-1024x583.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-item-details-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-item-details-0a-768x437.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-item-details-0a-1536x875.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-item-details-0a.webp 1895w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-save-changes" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Save Changes</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After making updates, click <strong>Save &amp; Continue</strong>.</li><li>A confirmation prompt will appear. Click <strong>Okay</strong> to apply the updates.</li><li>A success message will confirm that the food item has been updated.</li></ul><p></p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                24 => [
                    'id' => 25,
                    'doc_page_id' => 180,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide will walk you through the process of managing your food list in Menumium. You can filter, edit, perform bulk actions, and manage trash to keep your food items organized.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/8-4-1024x576.webp" alt="Manage Food List in Food Management" class="wp-image-9538" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/8-4-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/8-4-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/8-4-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/8-4-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/8-4.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-the-food-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to the Food List</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the main dashboard, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management &gt; Food Management</strong> in the left sidebar.</li><li>Click on Food Setup to open the food list page.</li></ul><h2 id="step-2-use-bulk-actions-filters" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Use Bulk Actions &amp; Filters</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select All: Check all food items at once to change their status or move them to trash.</li><li>Export Data: Click Export to download your food list for reports or records.</li><li>Filter Items: Click Filter to refine the list by:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Status (Active/Inactive)</li><li>Category</li><li>Creation Date / Modification Date</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="step-3-manage-individual-items" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Manage Individual Items</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Quick View: Click the Quick View (eye icon) to see item details in a side panel. From here you can:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Toggle the status (Active/Inactive)</li><li>Move the item to Trash</li></ul></li><li>Edit Details: Click the three-dot menu (…) &gt; Edit Details to fully edit the food item, including its name, price, variations, add-ons, and recipe.</li></ul><h2 id="step-4-import-food-data" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Import Food Data</h2><p>If you have an existing food list, click the Import button to bulk upload items directly into Menumium.</p><h2 id="step-5-manage-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Manage Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click View Trash on the food list page to see deleted items.</li><li>From here, you can either Restore an item back to the active list or Permanently Delete it.</li></ul><p>By managing your food list effectively, you ensure your menu stays organized, accurate, and customer-friendly.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                25 => [
                    'id' => 26,
                    'doc_page_id' => 181,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This documentation outlines the steps to create a cuisine from the Menumium admin dashboard.</p><div class="wp-block-group doc-tip"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong><em>Note</em></strong></p><p><em>Before starting this process, ensure the </em><strong><em><a href="https://menumium.com/documentation/food-management/">Food Setup</a></em></strong><em> is completed.</em></p></div></div><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-the-cuisine-setup-page" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to the Cuisine Setup Page</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dashboard, go to the <strong>side menu</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>Menu Setup Management &gt; Food Management</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Navigate Menu Setup" class="wp-image-11192" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Navigate Food Management" class="wp-image-11193" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a.webp 1906w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A drop-down menu will appear. Select <strong>Cuisine Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Navigate Cuisine" class="wp-image-11194" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-add-a-new-cuisine" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Add a New Cuisine</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Cuisine List</strong> page, click the <strong>Create Cuisine</strong> button located in the top-right corner.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cusine-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Cusine Button" class="wp-image-11195" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cusine-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cusine-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cusine-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cusine-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cusine-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A <strong>Create Cuisine</strong> pop-up window will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Copy-of-create-cuisine-1024x579.webp" alt="Create Cuisine
" class="wp-image-9519" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Copy-of-create-cuisine-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Copy-of-create-cuisine-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Copy-of-create-cuisine-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Copy-of-create-cuisine-1536x868.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Copy-of-create-cuisine.webp 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-fill-in-the-cuisine-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Fill in the Cuisine Details</h2><p>In the pop-up form, provide the following details:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Cuisine Name</strong>: Enter the name of the cuisine (e.g., <em>Japanese, Italian, Thai</em>).</li><li><strong>Description</strong>: Add a brief description of the cuisine.</li><li><strong>Status</strong>: Toggle the switch to set the cuisine as <strong>Active</strong> or <strong>Inactive</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-details-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Cusine Details" class="wp-image-11196" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-details-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-details-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-details-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-details-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-details-0a.webp 1913w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-upload-a-cuisine-image" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Upload a Cuisine Image</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Browse</strong> or drag and drop an image file into the upload area.</li><li>Supported file formats: <strong>JPG, PNG, JPEG, WEBP</strong>.</li><li>Maximum file size: <strong>5 MB</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cuisine-image-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Cuisine Image" class="wp-image-11197" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cuisine-image-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cuisine-image-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cuisine-image-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cuisine-image-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cuisine-image-0a.webp 1914w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-finalize-and-save" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Finalize and Save</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After filling in all the details and uploading the image, click the <strong>Create</strong> button at the bottom of the pop-up.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cuisine-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Cuisine Button" class="wp-image-11198" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cuisine-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cuisine-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cuisine-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cuisine-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-cuisine-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success message — <em>“Cuisine added successfully!”</em> — will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Success Notification" class="wp-image-11199" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The new cuisine will now be listed on the <strong>Cuisine List</strong> page.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/new-cuisine-0a_-1024x576.webp" alt="New Cuisine" class="wp-image-11200" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/new-cuisine-0a_-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/new-cuisine-0a_-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/new-cuisine-0a_-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/new-cuisine-0a_-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/new-cuisine-0a_.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>You have successfully created a new cuisine in Menumium, which can now be used to organize and categorize your menu items.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                26 => [
                    'id' => 27,
                    'doc_page_id' => 182,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This documentation outlines the steps to manage a cuisine from the Menumium admin dashboard.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-the-cuisine-setup-page" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to the Cuisine Setup Page</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dashboard, go to the <strong>side menu</strong>.</li><li>Click on <strong>Menu Setup Management &gt; Food Management</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Navigate Menu Setup" class="wp-image-11192" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Navigate Food Management" class="wp-image-11193" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a.webp 1906w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Cuisine Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Navigate Cuisine" class="wp-image-11194" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-cuisine-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-access-cuisine-management-options" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Access Cuisine Management Options</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Cuisine List</strong> page, locate the cuisine you want to manage.</li><li>Click the <strong>three-dot menu</strong> icon next to the cuisine name.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-3-dots-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Cusine 3 Dots" class="wp-image-11203" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-3-dots-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-3-dots-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-3-dots-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-3-dots-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/cusine-3-dots-0a.webp 1916w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A dropdown menu will appear with the following options:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Status</strong></li><li><strong>Quick View</strong></li><li><strong>Rename</strong></li><li><strong>Edit Details</strong></li><li><strong>Move to Trash</strong></li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-menu-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Dropdown Menu" class="wp-image-11227" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-menu-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-menu-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-menu-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-menu-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-menu-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-change-the-cuisine-status" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Change the Cuisine Status</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Cuisine List</strong> page, use the <strong>status toggle switch</strong> next to the cuisine name.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Status Toggle" class="wp-image-11205" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-confirmation-pop-up-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Status Confirmation Pop Up" class="wp-image-11206" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-confirmation-pop-up-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-confirmation-pop-up-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-confirmation-pop-up-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-confirmation-pop-up-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-confirmation-pop-up-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Confirm</strong> to activate or deactivate the cuisine.</li></ul><h2 id="step-4-view-cuisine-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: View Cuisine Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Quick View</strong> to see details of a cuisine.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Quick View Button" class="wp-image-11207" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up window will display:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Status</li><li>Cuisine Name</li><li>Creation Date</li><li>Description</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-pop-up-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Quick View Pop Up" class="wp-image-11208" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-pop-up-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-pop-up-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-pop-up-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-pop-up-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-pop-up-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-rename-a-cuisine" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Rename a Cuisine</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Rename</strong> from the three-dot menu.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Rename Button" class="wp-image-11209" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up will appear with a field to enter the new name.</li><li>Type the new cuisine name and click <strong>Save</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Rename Cuisine" class="wp-image-11211" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-cuisine-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-cuisine-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-cuisine-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-cuisine-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-edit-cuisine-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Edit Cuisine Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Edit Details</strong> from the dropdown menu.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Details Button" class="wp-image-11213" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up window titled <strong>Update Cuisine</strong> will appear.</li><li>Here, you can update:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Cuisine Name</strong></li><li><strong>Description</strong></li><li><strong>Cuisine Image</strong></li></ul></li><li>Click <strong>Update</strong> to save the changes.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Update Cuisine" class="wp-image-11214" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-cuisine-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-cuisine-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-cuisine-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-cuisine-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-cuisine-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-7-delete-a-cuisine" class="wp-block-heading">Step 7: Delete a Cuisine</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the three-dot menu, select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1-1024x576.webp" alt="Move To Trash" class="wp-image-11218" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-0a-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li><li>Click <strong>Trash</strong> to confirm and move the cuisine to the trash.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Trash Confirmation Popup" class="wp-image-11219" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-popup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-popup-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-popup-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-confirmation-popup-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-8-restore-or-delete-cuisine-from-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step-8: Restore or Delete Cuisine From Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>To restore a specific cuisine, click the <strong>View Trash</strong> button at the top of the Cuisine Setup Page.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="View Trash Button" class="wp-image-11220" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The Cuisine Trash List will display all deleted cuisines. Locate the cuisine you want to restore and click the restore icon</li><li>You’ll see two options: a circular arrow (restore) and a delete icon (permanent delete).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="571" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-and-delete-icon-0a-1024x571.webp" alt="Restore And Delete Icon" class="wp-image-11222" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-and-delete-icon-0a-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-and-delete-icon-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-and-delete-icon-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-and-delete-icon-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-and-delete-icon-0a.webp 1909w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Clicking the Delete icon will remove the cuisine permanently, and it cannot be restored afterward.</li><li>If you click the circular arrow, a confirmation window titled <em>Send back cuisine list</em> will appear. Click the green <strong>Send Back</strong> button to confirm.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-msg-0a-1024x573.webp" alt="Send Back Msg" class="wp-image-11223" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-msg-0a-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-msg-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-msg-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-msg-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-msg-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success message will appear at the bottom-left of the screen, and the cuisine will be restored to the main Cuisine List.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Success Msg" class="wp-image-11225" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>You have now learned how to <strong>view, edit, rename, activate/deactivate, and delete cuisines</strong> in Menumium for effective menu organization.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                27 => [
                    'id' => 28,
                    'doc_page_id' => 183,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This documentation outlines the steps to create a label from the Menumium admin dashboard.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-the-label-setup-page" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to the Label Setup Page</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>dashboard</strong>, go to the <strong>side menu</strong>.</li></ul><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click on <strong>Menu Setup Management &gt; Food Management</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Navigate Menu Setup" class="wp-image-11192" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Navigate Food Management" class="wp-image-11193" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a.webp 1906w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A dropdown menu will appear. Select <strong>Label Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Label Setup" class="wp-image-11233" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-add-a-new-label" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Add a New Label</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Label List</strong> page, click the <strong>Create Label</strong> button located at the top-right corner.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Label Button" class="wp-image-11235" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A <strong>Create Label</strong> pop-up window will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-pop-up-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Label Pop Up" class="wp-image-11236" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-pop-up-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-pop-up-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-pop-up-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-pop-up-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-pop-up-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-fill-in-the-label-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Fill in the Label Details</h2><p>In the pop-up window, provide the following information:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Label Name</strong>: Enter the name of the label (e.g., <em>Organic, Sugar-Free, Spicy</em>).</li><li><strong>Description</strong>: Add a brief description of the label.</li><li><strong>Status</strong>: Use the toggle switch to set the label as <em>Active</em> or <em>Inactive</em>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-description-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Label Description" class="wp-image-11237" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-description-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-description-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-description-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-description-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-label-description-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-upload-a-label-image" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Upload a Label Image</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click on <strong>Browse</strong> or drag and drop an image file into the designated area.</li><li>Supported formats: <strong>JPG, PNG, JPEG, WEBP</strong> (maximum size <strong>5 MB</strong>).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-image-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Label Image" class="wp-image-11238" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-image-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-image-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-image-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-image-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-image-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-finalize-and-save" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Finalize and Save</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After filling in all details and uploading the image, click the <strong>Create</strong> button at the bottom of the pop-up.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-label-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Create New Label" class="wp-image-11239" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-label-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-label-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-label-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-label-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-new-label-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success message, <strong>“Label added successfully!”</strong>, will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1-1024x576.webp" alt="Success Msg" class="wp-image-11240" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-msg-0a-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The new label will now be visible on the <strong>Label List</strong> page under <em>Customized Label</em>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="569" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/custom-label-0a-1024x569.webp" alt="Custom Label" class="wp-image-11242" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/custom-label-0a-1024x569.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/custom-label-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/custom-label-0a-768x426.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/custom-label-0a-1536x853.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/custom-label-0a.webp 1916w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>You have now successfully created a <strong>custom label</strong> that can be applied to your food items for better categorization and visibility.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                28 => [
                    'id' => 29,
                    'doc_page_id' => 184,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Managing labels allows you to highlight specific characteristics of menu items, such as <strong>Organic</strong>, <strong>Veg</strong>, or <strong>Gluten-Free</strong>, to help customers make informed choices. The Menumium system includes a set of default labels that can be managed and filtered.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-label-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Label Setup</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>dashboard</strong>, click on <strong>Menu Setup Management</strong> in the left-side navigation panel.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Navigate Menu Setup" class="wp-image-11192" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Navigate Food Management" class="wp-image-11193" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a.webp 1906w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Label Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Label Setup" class="wp-image-11233" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-change-label-status" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Change Label Status</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the default label (e.g., <em>Organic, Veg</em>).</li><li>Click on the <strong>three dots</strong> (â®) to the right of the label.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Status</strong> to toggle the label on or off.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-label-3-dots-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Default Label 3 Dots" class="wp-image-11246" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-label-3-dots-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-label-3-dots-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-label-3-dots-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-label-3-dots-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-label-3-dots-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear; click <strong>Confirm</strong> to proceed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-label-status-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Confirmation Pop Up Label Status" class="wp-image-11247" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-label-status-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-label-status-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-label-status-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-label-status-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-label-status-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-view-label-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: View Label Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click on the <strong>three dots</strong> (â®) next to a label.</li><li>Select <strong>Quick View</strong> to open a detailed pop-up.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Quick View" class="wp-image-11248" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The pop-up will display the label’s <strong>image, description, and status</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0a-1024x573.webp" alt="Quick View Details" class="wp-image-11249" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0a-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0a-768x429.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0a-1536x859.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-filter-labels" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Filter Labels</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Label List page, click the <strong>Filter</strong> button in the top-right corner.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-label-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Filter Label" class="wp-image-11250" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-label-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-label-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-label-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-label-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-label-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The filter pop-up allows you to refine results using:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Status</strong>: All, Active, or Inactive.</li><li><strong>Foods Using This Label</strong>.</li><li><strong>Creation Date / Modified Date</strong>.</li><li><strong>Sort Order</strong>: Newest to Oldest, Oldest to Newest, Last Updated.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-details-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Filter Details" class="wp-image-11251" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-details-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-details-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-details-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-details-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After selecting your filters, click <strong>Apply</strong> to view the results.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-apply-0a-1024x573.webp" alt="Filter Apply" class="wp-image-11252" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-apply-0a-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-apply-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-apply-0a-768x429.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-apply-0a-1536x859.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/filter-apply-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>With these options, you can easily manage <strong>default labels</strong> to ensure your menu items are categorized and highlighted for customers in the best possible way.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                29 => [
                    'id' => 30,
                    'doc_page_id' => 185,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This documentation outlines the steps to manage <strong>customized labels</strong> from the Menumium admin dashboard.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-the-label-setup-page" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to the Label Setup Page</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the <strong>dashboard</strong>, go to the left-hand side menu.</li><li>Click on <strong>Menu Setup Management &gt; Food Management</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Navigate Menu Setup" class="wp-image-11192" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-menu-setup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Navigate Food Management" class="wp-image-11193" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-food-management-0a.webp 1906w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A dropdown menu will appear. Select <strong>Label Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Label Setup" class="wp-image-11233" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-setup-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The <strong>Label List</strong> page will display two sections: <em>Default Label</em> and <em>Customized Label</em>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-and-customized-label-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Default And Customized Label" class="wp-image-11257" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-and-customized-label-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-and-customized-label-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-and-customized-label-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-and-customized-label-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/default-and-customized-label-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-change-the-label-status" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Change the Label Status</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Label List page, use the <strong>toggle switch</strong> next to the label to activate or deactivate it.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-0a-1024x577.webp" alt="Label Status" class="wp-image-11259" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-0a-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-0a-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear. Click <strong>Confirm</strong> to proceed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-confirm-0a-1024x577.webp" alt="Label Status Confirm" class="wp-image-11260" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-confirm-0a-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-confirm-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-confirm-0a-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-confirm-0a-1536x866.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-status-confirm-0a.webp 1914w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-view-label-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: View Label Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Quick View</strong> from the three-dot menu (â®).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="578" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-quick-view-0a-1024x578.webp" alt="Label Quick View" class="wp-image-11261" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-quick-view-0a-1024x578.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-quick-view-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-quick-view-0a-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-quick-view-0a-1536x868.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-quick-view-0a.webp 1910w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up window will display the label’s <strong>name, type, status, and creation date</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="580" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0b-1024x580.webp" alt="Quick View Details" class="wp-image-11262" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0b-1024x580.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0b-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0b-768x435.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0b-1536x870.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/quick-view-details-0b.webp 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From this pop-up, you can also toggle the status or move the label to trash or edit it.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="580" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-and-delete-from-quick-view-0a-1024x580.webp" alt="Status And Delete From Quick View" class="wp-image-11263" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-and-delete-from-quick-view-0a-1024x580.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-and-delete-from-quick-view-0a-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-and-delete-from-quick-view-0a-768x435.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-and-delete-from-quick-view-0a-1536x870.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-and-delete-from-quick-view-0a.webp 1904w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-rename-a-customized-label" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Rename a Customized Label</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the three-dot menu (â®), select <strong>Rename</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Rename" class="wp-image-11264" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up will appear with a field to enter the new name.</li><li>Enter the new name and click <strong>Save</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-field-and-save-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Rename Field And Save" class="wp-image-11265" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-field-and-save-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-field-and-save-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-field-and-save-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-field-and-save-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-field-and-save-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-edit-a-customized-label" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Edit a Customized Label</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Under the <strong>Customized Label</strong> section, locate the label you want to manage.</li><li>Click the <strong>three-dot menu</strong> (â®) next to the label.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="569" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customized-label-3-dots-0a-1024x569.webp" alt="Customized Label 3 Dots" class="wp-image-11258" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customized-label-3-dots-0a-1024x569.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customized-label-3-dots-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customized-label-3-dots-0a-768x427.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customized-label-3-dots-0a-1536x854.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/customized-label-3-dots-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Edit Details</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-edit-details-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Label Edit Details" class="wp-image-11266" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-edit-details-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-edit-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-edit-details-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-edit-details-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/label-edit-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up window named <strong>Update Label</strong> will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="578" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-0a-1024x578.webp" alt="Update Label" class="wp-image-11267" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-0a-1024x578.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-0a-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-0a-1536x868.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-0a.webp 1910w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Modify the <strong>Label Name, Description, or Label Image</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="583" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-details-0a-1024x583.webp" alt="Update Label Details" class="wp-image-11268" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-details-0a-1024x583.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-details-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-details-0a-768x437.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-details-0a-1536x874.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-label-details-0a.webp 1892w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Update</strong> to save your changes.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="584" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1024x584.webp" alt="Update Button" class="wp-image-11269" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1024x584.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-768x438.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1536x876.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a.webp 1893w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-move-a-label-to-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Move a Label to Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the three-dot menu (â®), select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-3-points-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Move To Trash 3 Points" class="wp-image-11270" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-3-points-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-3-points-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-3-points-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-3-points-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-3-points-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li><li>Click <strong>Trash</strong> to confirm the deletion and move the label to trash.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Delete Confirmation" class="wp-image-11275" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-7-delete-label-permanently" class="wp-block-heading">Step 7: Delete Label Permanently </h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Label List page, click the <strong>View Trash</strong> button.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-1024x576.webp" alt="View Trash Button" class="wp-image-11272" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The trash list will appear, showing all deleted labels.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Trash List" class="wp-image-11273" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the label you want to delete and click the <strong>Delete Icon.</strong></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0a-1024x577.webp" alt="Delete Icon" class="wp-image-11274" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0a-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0a-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-0a.webp 1916w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the pop-up, click Delete to delete the customized label permanently.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Delete Confirmation" class="wp-image-11275" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-confirmation-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-8-restore-a-label-from-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 8: Restore a Label from Trash</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Label List page, click the <strong>View Trash</strong> button.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-1024x576.webp" alt="View Trash Button" class="wp-image-11272" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-button-0a-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The trash list will appear, showing all deleted labels.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Trash List" class="wp-image-11273" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the label you want to restore and click the <strong>restore icon</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1-1024x575.webp" alt="Restore Icon" class="wp-image-11276" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-1.webp 1914w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>In the pop-up, click <strong>Send Back</strong> to restore the label to the Customized Label list.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1-1024x573.webp" alt="Send Back" class="wp-image-11277" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-0a-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success notification will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="580" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1-1024x580.webp" alt="Success Notification" class="wp-image-11278" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1-1024x580.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1-768x435.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1-1536x870.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-1.webp 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>By following these steps, you can <strong>edit, rename, activate, delete, or restore customized labels</strong>, ensuring your menu is always up-to-date and tailored to your needs.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                30 => [
                    'id' => 31,
                    'doc_page_id' => 186,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Menu types allow you to categorize your offerings in different ways, such as <strong>“Popular Menu,” “Seasonal Specials,” or “Kids Menu.”</strong> This guide will walk you through the process of creating a new menu type.</p><div class="wp-block-group doc-tip"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong>Note</strong></p><p>Before starting, ensure the <strong>Food Setup</strong> is completed. A default menu is automatically created with a default branch.</p></div></div><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Menu Type</h2><p>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management</strong> → <strong>Food Management</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Setup Management" class="wp-image-11285" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Management Nav" class="wp-image-11286" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>From the dropdown, select <strong>Menu Type</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Type Setup" class="wp-image-11287" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-create-a-new-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Create a New Menu Type</h2><p>On the <strong>Menu Type List</strong> page, click the <strong>Create Menu Type</strong> button in the top-right corner.<br>A pop-up window will appear with input fields.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-create-button-1024x575.webp" alt="Menu Type Create Button" class="wp-image-11288" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-create-button-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-create-button-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-create-button-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-create-button-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-create-button.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="582" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-pop-up-1024x582.webp" alt="Menu Type Pop Up" class="wp-image-11289" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-pop-up-1024x582.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-pop-up-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-pop-up-768x437.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-pop-up-1536x874.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-pop-up.webp 1897w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-fill-in-menu-type-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Fill in Menu Type Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Menu Type Name:</strong> Enter a name for the new menu type (e.g., “Popular Menu”).</li><li><strong>Description:</strong> Add a short description for clarity.</li><li><strong>Menu Type Status: </strong>Toggle menu type status on or off.</li><li><strong>Menu Type Image:</strong> Click <strong>Browse</strong> (or drag &amp; drop) to upload an image for the menu type.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="582" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-details-1024x582.webp" alt="Menu Type Details" class="wp-image-11290" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-details-1024x582.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-details-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-details-768x436.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-details-1536x873.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-details.webp 1899w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>Once all fields are completed, click <strong>Create</strong> to save the new menu type.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-type-create-button-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Menu Type Create Button" class="wp-image-11291" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-type-create-button-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-type-create-button-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-type-create-button-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-type-create-button-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-type-create-button.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-view-the-new-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: View the New Menu Type</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After creating, a confirmation message will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-confirmation-message-1024x577.webp" alt="Create Confirmation Message" class="wp-image-11292" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-confirmation-message-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-confirmation-message-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-confirmation-message-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-confirmation-message-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-confirmation-message.webp 1916w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Your new menu type will now be listed under the <strong>Menu Type List</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/created-menu-type-1024x576.webp" alt="Created Menu Type" class="wp-image-11293" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/created-menu-type-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/created-menu-type-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/created-menu-type-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/created-menu-type-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/created-menu-type.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>You’ve successfully created a new menu type, which can now be used to organize and showcase your food offerings.</p><p></p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                31 => [
                    'id' => 32,
                    'doc_page_id' => 187,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide will show you how to manage existing menu types, including editing details, changing their status, renaming, and deleting them.</p><p class="doc-tip"><strong>Note</strong></p><p>Before starting, ensure the <a href="https://menumium.com/documentation/food-management/"><strong>Food Setup</strong></a> is completed. A default menu is automatically created with a default branch.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Menu Type</h2><p>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management</strong> → <strong>Food Management</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Setup Management" class="wp-image-11285" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Management Nav" class="wp-image-11286" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>From the dropdown, select <strong>Menu Type</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Type Setup" class="wp-image-11287" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-access-menu-type-options" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Access Menu Type Options</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Menu Type List</strong> page, locate the menu type you want to manage.</li><li>Click the <strong>three dots icon (â®)</strong> on the right side of the entry. A dropdown menu will appear with the following options:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Status:</strong> Toggle the menu type on or off.</li><li><strong>View Details:</strong> View more information about the menu type.</li><li><strong>Rename:</strong> Change the menu type name.</li><li><strong>Edit Details:</strong> Update the name, description, or image.</li><li><strong>Move to Trash:</strong> Delete the menu type.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-3-dots-1024x577.webp" alt="Menu Type 3 Dots" class="wp-image-11294" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-3-dots-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-3-dots-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-3-dots-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-3-dots-1536x866.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-3-dots.webp 1914w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p></p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                32 => [
                    'id' => 33,
                    'doc_page_id' => 188,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to assign a food item to an existing menu type in Menumium. Assigning menu types helps you organize your offerings into categories such as <strong>Popular Menu</strong>, <strong>Seasonal Specials</strong>, or <strong>Kids Menu</strong>, making it easier for customers to browse.</p><div class="wp-block-group doc-tip"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong>Note</strong></p><p>Before starting, ensure the <a href="https://menumium.com/documentation/food-management/"><strong>Food Setup</strong></a> is completed. A default menu is automatically created with a default branch.</p></div></div><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-food-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Food Setup</h2><p>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management</strong> → <strong>Food Management</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Setup Management" class="wp-image-11285" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Management Nav" class="wp-image-11286" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p><br>Click on <strong>Food Setup</strong> from the dropdown menu.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-1024x574.webp" alt="Food Setup" class="wp-image-11295" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-select-food-item-to-edit" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Select Food Item to Edit</h2><p>On the <strong>Food List</strong> page, locate the food item you want to assign to a menu type.</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click the <strong>three dots icon (â®)</strong> on the right-hand side of the food entry.</li><li>From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Edit Details</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-edit-details-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Food Setup Edit Details 0a" class="wp-image-11296" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-edit-details-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-edit-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-edit-details-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-edit-details-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-setup-edit-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-assign-a-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Assign a Menu Type</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Edit <strong>Details</strong></strong> page, scroll down to the <strong>Select Menu Type</strong> section.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-menu-type-1024x576.webp" alt="Select Menu Type" class="wp-image-11297" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-menu-type-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-menu-type-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-menu-type-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-menu-type-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-menu-type.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Open the dropdown menu and select one or more menu types (e.g., <em>Seasonal Menu</em>, <em>Popular Menu</em>).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Dropdown" class="wp-image-11298" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/dropdown-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Once done, click <strong>Save &amp; Continue</strong> at the bottom of the page.</li></ul><p>The food item is now successfully assigned to the selected menu type and will appear under that category in your customer-facing menu.</p><h2 id="step-4-change-menu-type-status" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Change Menu Type Status</h2><p>To activate or deactivate a menu type:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click the <strong>Status toggle</strong> switch.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1-1024x576.webp" alt="Status Toggle" class="wp-image-11299" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/status-toggle-0a-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-0a-1024x577.webp" alt="Confirmation Pop Up" class="wp-image-11300" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-0a-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-0a-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirmation-pop-up-0a.webp 1916w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Confirm</strong> to proceed.</li></ul><div class="wp-block-group doc-tip"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong>Note</strong></p><p>Inactive menu types will not appear on your public menu.</p></div></div><h2 id="step-5-view-menu-type-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: View Menu Type Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>View Details</strong> to see an overview.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Rename From Dropdown" class="wp-image-11303" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a.webp 1911w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The pop-up displays <strong>Name, Status, Creation Date, and Number of Food Items</strong> using this menu type.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="571" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1024x571.webp" alt="Detailed View Details" class="wp-image-11302" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a.webp 1912w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From here, click <strong>Edit Menu Type</strong> to make changes, or <strong>Close</strong> to exit.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-or-cancel-0a-1024x577.webp" alt="Edit or Cancel" class="wp-image-11344" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-or-cancel-0a-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-or-cancel-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-or-cancel-0a-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-or-cancel-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-or-cancel-0a.webp 1916w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-rename-a-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Rename a Menu Type</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Choose <strong>Rename</strong> from the dropdown.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Rename From Dropdown" class="wp-image-11303" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a-1536x855.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-from-dropdown-0a.webp 1911w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Enter the new name and click <strong>Save</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/save-rename-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Save Rename" class="wp-image-11304" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/save-rename-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/save-rename-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/save-rename-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/save-rename-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/save-rename-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-7-edit-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 7: Edit Details</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-menu-type-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Details Menu Type" class="wp-image-11305" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-menu-type-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-menu-type-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-menu-type-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-menu-type-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-details-menu-type-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Change the <strong>Menu Type Name</strong>.</li><li>Add or update the <strong>Description</strong>.</li><li>Upload a new <strong>Menu Type Image</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Update</strong> to save changes.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-menu-type-details-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Update Menu Type Details" class="wp-image-11306" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-menu-type-details-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-menu-type-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-menu-type-details-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-menu-type-details-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-menu-type-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>You’ve now learned how to manage menu types effectively—keeping them updated, organized, and relevant for your customers.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                33 => [
                    'id' => 34,
                    'doc_page_id' => 189,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to temporarily remove a menu type by moving it to the trash and how to restore it if needed.</p><h2 id="part-1-delete-a-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Part 1: Delete a Menu Type</h2><h3 id="step-1-open-menu-type-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Open Menu Type List</h3><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the dashboard, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management → Food Management → Menu Type</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Setup Management" class="wp-image-11285" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-management.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Management Nav" class="wp-image-11286" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Type Setup" class="wp-image-11287" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-setup.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The Menu Type List page will display all existing menu types.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-list-page-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Menu Type List Page" class="wp-image-11307" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-list-page-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-list-page-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-list-page-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-list-page-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-type-list-page-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h3 id="step-2-move-a-menu-type-to-trash" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Move a Menu Type to Trash</h3><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the menu type you want to delete.</li><li>Click the <strong>three-dot icon</strong> on its card.</li><li>From the dropdown, select <strong>Move to Trash</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-icon-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Move To Trash Icon" class="wp-image-11308" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-icon-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-icon-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-icon-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-icon-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/move-to-trash-icon-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h3 id="step-3-confirm-deletion" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Confirm Deletion</h3><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear.</li><li>Click the <strong>red Trash button</strong> to confirm.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-popup-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Confirm Deletion Popup" class="wp-image-11309" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-popup-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-popup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-popup-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-popup-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/confirm-deletion-popup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The menu type will now be removed from the main list and stored in the Trash.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-success-popup-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Trash Success Popup" class="wp-image-11310" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-success-popup-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-success-popup-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-success-popup-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-success-popup-0a-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/trash-success-popup-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="part-2-restore-a-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Part 2: Restore a Menu Type</h2><h3 id="step-1-access-the-trash-list" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Access the Trash List</h3><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Menu Type List page, click the <strong>View Trash</strong> button at the top.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="571" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1-1024x571.webp" alt="View Trash" class="wp-image-11311" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1-1536x857.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-0a-1.webp 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>This will display all deleted menu types under Menu Type Trash List.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="View Trash List" class="wp-image-11312" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-list-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-list-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-list-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-trash-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h3 id="step-2-restore-or-permanently-delete-the-menu-type" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Restore or Permanently Delete the Menu Type</h3><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the menu type you wish to restore.</li><li>Click the <strong>restore option</strong> (circular arrow).</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="571" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-2-1024x571.webp" alt="Restore Icon" class="wp-image-11313" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-2-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-2-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-2-768x429.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-2-1536x857.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/restore-icon-0a-2.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h3 id="step-3-confirm-restoration" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Confirm Restoration</h3><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation window titled <em>Send back menu type list</em> will appear.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-menu-type-list-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Send Back Menu Type List" class="wp-image-11314" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-menu-type-list-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-menu-type-list-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-menu-type-list-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-menu-type-list-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-menu-type-list-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click the <strong>green Send Back button</strong> to confirm.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-button-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Send Back Button" class="wp-image-11315" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-button-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-button-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-button-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-button-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/send-back-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h3 id="step-4-success-message" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Success Message</h3><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A success notification will appear at the bottom-left of the screen.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-2-1024x575.webp" alt="Success Notification" class="wp-image-11316" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-2-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-2-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-2-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-2-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/success-notification-0a-2.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The restored menu type will now reappear in the main Menu Type List.</li><li>Clicking the Delete icon will remove the Menu Type permanently, and it cannot be restored afterward.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-menu-type-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Delete Icon Menu Type" class="wp-image-11317" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-menu-type-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-menu-type-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-menu-type-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-menu-type-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/delete-icon-menu-type-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>This way, you can safely manage menu types—removing them temporarily or permanently  when not needed and restoring them later without data loss.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                34 => [
                    'id' => 35,
                    'doc_page_id' => 190,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide will show you how to create a new menu and assign it to one or more branches in Menumium.</p><div class="wp-block-group doc-tip"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong>Note</strong></p><p><em><em>Before starting this process, ensure the</em><a href="https://menumium.com/documentation/food-management/"><em> </em><strong><em>Food Setup</em></strong></a><em> is completed. A default menu is automatically created with a default branch.</em></em></p></div></div><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-menu-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Menu Management</h2><p>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management</strong> and click on <strong>Menu Management</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Menu Setup Navigation" class="wp-image-11400" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Management Nav" class="wp-image-11401" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-create-a-new-menu" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Create a New Menu</h2><p>From the Menu Management page, click the green <strong>Create Menu</strong> button in the top-right corner, next to <strong>Menu List</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="573" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-button-0b-1024x573.webp" alt="Create Menu Button" class="wp-image-11402" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-button-0b-1024x573.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-button-0b-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-button-0b-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-button-0b-1536x860.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-button-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-fill-in-menu-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Fill in Menu Details</h2><p>A <strong>Create Menu</strong> pop-up will appear. Enter the required details:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Menu Name:</strong> Type the name of the new menu.</li><li><strong>Select Branch Name:</strong> Choose the branch(es) where this menu will be active. You can assign multiple branches.</li><li><strong>Status:</strong> Use the toggle to activate or deactivate the menu. (Active menus are visible to customers.)</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-popup-form-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Create Menu Popup Form" class="wp-image-11403" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-popup-form-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-popup-form-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-popup-form-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-popup-form-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-menu-popup-form-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-save-the-new-menu" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Save the New Menu</h2><p>Click the green <strong>Create</strong> button to finalize.</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation message will appear at the bottom of your screen.</li><li>Your new menu is now created.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-button-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="Create Button" class="wp-image-11404" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-button-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-button-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-button-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-button-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/create-button-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-select-categories-food-items" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Select Categories &amp; Food Items</h2><p>After creating the menu:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select food <strong>categories</strong> and save them.</li></ul><p>You have successfully created a new menu, assigned it to branches, and prepared it for category and food item setup.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Select Categories &amp; Food" class="wp-image-11405" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From this page, you can also <strong>edit categories</strong> as needed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-items-0c.webp" alt="Select Categories &amp; Food Items" class="wp-image-11413" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-items-0c.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-items-0c-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-categories-and-food-items-0c-768x431.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>You have successfully created a new menu, assigned it to branches, and prepared it for category and food item setup.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                35 => [
                    'id' => 36,
                    'doc_page_id' => 191,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>The <strong>Menu Management</strong> section allows you to manage all aspects of your menu, including categories, food items, and settings. This guide will walk you through the process of editing food items within an existing menu.</p><div class="wp-block-group doc-tip"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong>Note</strong></p><p><em><em>Before starting, make sure the </em><a href="https://menumium.com/documentation/food-management/"><strong><em>Food Setup</em></strong></a><em> is completed. A default menu is automatically created with a default branch.</em></em></p></div></div><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-menu-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Menu Management</h2><p>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management</strong> and click on <strong>Menu Management</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Menu Setup Navigation" class="wp-image-11400" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Management Nav" class="wp-image-11401" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-select-a-menu-to-edit" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Select a Menu to Edit</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>You will see a list of your existing menus.</li><li>Click on the <strong>Edit Menu Food</strong> icon next to the menu you want to modify.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Menu Food" class="wp-image-11408" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-access-food-item-options" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Access Food Item Options</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the <strong>category</strong> containing the food you want to edit.</li><li>You can toggle or delete the entire category if required.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-details-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Menu Food Details" class="wp-image-11409" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-details-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-details-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-details-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>For individual food items, click on the <strong>three dots (â®)</strong> on the right side of the item to open the options menu.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-food-items-3-dots-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Food Items 3 Dots" class="wp-image-11410" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-food-items-3-dots-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-food-items-3-dots-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-food-items-3-dots-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-food-items-3-dots-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-food-items-3-dots-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-change-item-status-active-inactive" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Change Item Status (Active/Inactive)</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Use the <strong>Status toggle</strong> to activate or deactivate a food item.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1910" height="1079" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-status-0a.webp" alt="Food Item Status" class="wp-image-11417" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-status-0a.webp 1910w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-status-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-status-0a-1024x578.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-status-0a-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-status-0a-1536x868.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1910px) 100vw, 1910px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation pop-up will appear—click <strong>Confirm</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/turn-off-food-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Turn Off Food Confirmation" class="wp-image-11418" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/turn-off-food-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/turn-off-food-confirmation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/turn-off-food-confirmation-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/turn-off-food-confirmation-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/turn-off-food-confirmation-0a.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Inactive items will not appear on your public menu.</li></ul><h2 id="step-5-quick-view-food-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Quick View Food Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Quick View</strong> from the menu options.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-quick-view-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Food Item Quick View" class="wp-image-11419" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-quick-view-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-quick-view-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-quick-view-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-quick-view-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-item-quick-view-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up will show key details of the food item, such as <strong>price, category, stock, variations, add-ons, labels, and cuisine,</strong> and <strong>status toggle</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Food Details" class="wp-image-11420" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-edit-food-price" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Edit Food Price</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Edit Price</strong> from the options.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-price-0b-1024x575.webp" alt="Edit Price" class="wp-image-11421" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-price-0b-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-price-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-price-0b-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-price-0b-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-price-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Enter the new price in the provided field.</li><li>Click <strong>Update</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-edit-price-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Update Edit Price" class="wp-image-11422" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-edit-price-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-edit-price-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-edit-price-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-edit-price-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-edit-price-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A confirmation message will notify you that this change applies to all branches using this menu. Click <strong>Okay</strong> to proceed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Update Price Confirmation" class="wp-image-11423" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-confirmation-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-confirmation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-confirmation-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-confirmation-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-confirmation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-7-edit-discount" class="wp-block-heading">Step 7: Edit Discount</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-discount-0d-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Discount" class="wp-image-11424" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-discount-0d-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-discount-0d-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-discount-0d-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-discount-0d-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-discount-0d.webp 1918w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Toggle <strong>Update Discount</strong> to add or change a discount.</li><li>You can set a <strong>percentage or fixed amount</strong>, and define a <strong>validity period</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Update</strong> to save.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-discount-confirmation-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Update Discount Confirmation" class="wp-image-11425" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-discount-confirmation-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-discount-confirmation-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-discount-confirmation-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-discount-confirmation-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-discount-confirmation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-8-edit-stock" class="wp-block-heading">Step 8: Edit Stock</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select <strong>Edit Stock</strong> from the options.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Stock" class="wp-image-11426" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Choose between <strong>Unlimited</strong> or <strong>Limited</strong> stock from the <strong>Stock Type</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Update</strong> to apply changes</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-stock-confirmation-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Update Stock Confirmation" class="wp-image-11427" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-stock-confirmation-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-stock-confirmation-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-stock-confirmation-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-stock-confirmation-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-stock-confirmation-0a.webp 1913w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p>You have successfully edited food items in your menu, including status, price, discounts, and stock.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                    'updated_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
                ],
                36 => [
                    'id' => 37,
                    'doc_page_id' => 192,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>The <strong>Menu Management</strong> section allows you to view, edit, and control existing menus. This includes changing their visibility, renaming them, editing food items, or deleting them entirely.</p><div class="wp-block-group doc-tip"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p><strong>Note</strong></p><p><em><em>Before starting, make sure the</em><a href="https://menumium.com/documentation/food-management/"><em> </em><strong><em>Food Setup</em></strong><em> </em></a><em>is completed. A default menu is automatically created with a default branch.</em></em></p></div></div><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-menu-management" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Menu Management</h2><p>From the left-hand menu, go to <strong>Menu Setup Management</strong> and click on <strong>Menu Management</strong>.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Menu Setup Navigation" class="wp-image-11400" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-setup-navigation-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Menu Management Nav" class="wp-image-11401" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-management-nav-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-change-menu-status-active-inactive" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Change Menu Status (Active/Inactive)</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Use the <strong>Status Toggle</strong> next to the menu’s name to switch it on or off.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="569" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-status-toggle-0a-1024x569.webp" alt="Menu Status Toggle" class="wp-image-11428" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-status-toggle-0a-1024x569.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-status-toggle-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-status-toggle-0a-768x427.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-status-toggle-0a-1536x853.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/menu-status-toggle-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>If the menu is currently assigned to branches, the system will prompt you to assign another menu:</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="577" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/shift-branch-to-another-menu-popup-0a-1024x577.webp" alt="Shift Branch to Another Menu Popup" class="wp-image-11429" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/shift-branch-to-another-menu-popup-0a-1024x577.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/shift-branch-to-another-menu-popup-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/shift-branch-to-another-menu-popup-0a-768x433.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/shift-branch-to-another-menu-popup-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/shift-branch-to-another-menu-popup-0a.webp 1912w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Select a new menu and click <strong>Choose &amp; Turn Off</strong>, or</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/change-menu-status-0c.webp" alt="Change Menu Status" class="wp-image-11439" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/change-menu-status-0c.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/change-menu-status-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/change-menu-status-0c-768x432.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Turn Off Without Changing</strong> to deactivate without assigning a replacement.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-and-turn-off-0a.webp" alt="Choose &amp; Turn Off" class="wp-image-11825" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-and-turn-off-0a.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-and-turn-off-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/choose-and-turn-off-0a-768x432.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-view-menu-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: View Menu Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Menu List</strong> page, locate the menu you want to manage.</li><li>Click the <strong>three dots (â®)</strong> under the Action column.</li><li>Select <strong>View Details</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="View Details Button" class="wp-image-11431" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0a-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/view-details-button-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up will show the menu’s status, creation date, and a full list of included food items.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1-1024x574.webp" alt="Detailed View Details" class="wp-image-11442" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/detailed-view-details-0a-1.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Close</strong> to exit, or <strong>Edit Menu</strong> to make changes.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/close-or-edit-menu-buttons-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Close or Edit Menu Buttons" class="wp-image-11443" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/close-or-edit-menu-buttons-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/close-or-edit-menu-buttons-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/close-or-edit-menu-buttons-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/close-or-edit-menu-buttons-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/close-or-edit-menu-buttons-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-rename-menu" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Rename Menu</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the Action menu (three dots), select <strong>Rename Menu</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-menu-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Rename Menu" class="wp-image-11444" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-menu-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-menu-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-menu-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-menu-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-menu-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Enter a new name for the menu, then click <strong>Save</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-and-save-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Rename &amp; Save" class="wp-image-11445" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-and-save-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-and-save-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-and-save-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-and-save-0a-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/rename-and-save-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-edit-menu-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Edit Menu Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the Action menu (three dots), select <strong>Edit Menu</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-button-0a-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Menu Button" class="wp-image-11446" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-button-0a-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-button-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-button-0a-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-button-0a-1536x865.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-button-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A pop-up will appear where you can:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Rename the Menu</strong> by entering a new name in the <em>Menu Name</em> field.</li><li><strong>Assign Branches</strong> by selecting one or more from the <em>Branch Name</em> dropdown.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-details-0a-1024x575.webp" alt="Edit Menu Details" class="wp-image-11447" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-details-0a-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-details-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-details-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-details-0a-1536x863.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-details-0a.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Click <strong>Update</strong> to save changes.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="575" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1-1024x575.webp" alt="Update Button" class="wp-image-11448" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1-1536x862.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-button-0a-1.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-6-edit-menu-food" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Edit Menu Food</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the Action menu, select <strong>Edit Menu Food</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="572" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-button-0a-1024x572.webp" alt="Edit Menu Food Button" class="wp-image-11449" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-button-0a-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-button-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-button-0a-768x429.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-button-0a-1536x858.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-menu-food-button-0a.webp 1911w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Here, you can:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Change category or food <strong>status (active/inactive)</strong>.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="570" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/category-toggle-0a-1024x570.webp" alt="Category Toggle" class="wp-image-11450" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/category-toggle-0a-1024x570.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/category-toggle-0a-300x167.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/category-toggle-0a-768x428.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/category-toggle-0a-1536x856.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/category-toggle-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-status-toggle-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Food Status Toggle" class="wp-image-11451" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-status-toggle-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-status-toggle-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-status-toggle-0a-768x431.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-status-toggle-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-status-toggle-0a.webp 1917w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>View details</strong> of each item.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-1024x576.webp" alt="Food Details" class="wp-image-11420" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/food-details-0c.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Update <strong>price</strong> or <strong>discounts</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="574" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-and-discount-0a-1024x574.webp" alt="Update Price &amp; Discount" class="wp-image-11452" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-and-discount-0a-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-and-discount-0a-300x168.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-and-discount-0a-768x430.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-and-discount-0a-1536x861.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/update-price-and-discount-0a.webp 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Manage <strong>stock availability</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-1024x576.webp" alt="Edit Stock" class="wp-image-11426" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-768x432.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/edit-stock-0b.webp 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><p></p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:16.000000Z',
