                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>Menumium makes online ordering fast and convenient. With just a few clicks, customers can browse the menu, add their favorite dishes, and place orders for delivery or pickup.</p><h2 id="step-1-browse-the-menu-and-add-items" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Browse the Menu and Add Items</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Visit the restaurant’s website to access the full menu.</li><li>Browse categories such as <strong>Popular Dishes, Burgers &amp; Wraps, Pizzas,</strong> and more.</li><li>To add an item, click the <strong>Add</strong> button.</li><li>A pop-up window will appear with item details. Adjust the quantity using the <strong>(– / +)</strong> buttons.</li><li>Click <strong>Add to Cart</strong> to confirm.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/browse-the-menu-and-add-items-0a.webp" alt="Browse The Menu And Add Items
" class="wp-image-10842" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/browse-the-menu-and-add-items-0a.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/browse-the-menu-and-add-items-0a-300x169.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/browse-the-menu-and-add-items-0a-768x432.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-proceed-to-checkout" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Proceed to Checkout</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Once all items are in your cart, look at the <strong>Cart Summary</strong> on the right-hand side.</li><li>Click the <strong>Checkout</strong> button to continue.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-cart-summary-1024x579.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-10164" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-cart-summary-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-cart-summary-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-cart-summary-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-cart-summary-1536x868.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-cart-summary.webp 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-enter-personal-and-delivery-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Enter Personal and Delivery Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the checkout page, fill in your <strong>Name, Email, and Phone Number.</strong></li><li>Select a <strong>Delivery Type:</strong><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Home Delivery:</strong> Enter your delivery address.</li><li><strong>Take Away:</strong> Choose this option if you plan to pick up your order.</li></ul></li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="581" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-personal-details-1024x581.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-10166" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-personal-details-1024x581.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-personal-details-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-personal-details-768x436.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-personal-details-1536x872.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/website-order-online-personal-details.webp 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-review-and-place-your-order" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Review and Place Your Order</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Check the <strong>Cart Summary</strong> to ensure all items and quantities are correct.</li><li>Apply a <strong>coupon code</strong> if available.</li><li>Click the <strong>Place Order</strong> button to complete your purchase.</li></ul><h2 id="step-5-order-confirmation-invoice" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Order Confirmation &amp; Invoice</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>After successful submission, a confirmation screen will display:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Your <strong>Order ID</strong></li><li>Expected <strong>delivery or pickup time</strong></li></ul></li><li>You can also download a <strong>PDF invoice</strong> by clicking <strong>Download Invoice.</strong></li></ul><p>Placing an online order with Menumium is simple—browse, customize, and checkout in just a few steps.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
