                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide explains how to assign a delivery man to a home delivery order in Menumium. Assigning ensures proper tracking and management of deliveries.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-online-orders" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Online Orders</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From your <strong>dashboard</strong>, go to the left-hand menu.</li><li>Click on <strong>Order Management</strong>.</li><li>Under it, select <strong>Online Orders</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="584" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-online-orders-0a-1024x584.webp" alt="Navigate To Online Orders" class="wp-image-11969" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-online-orders-0a-1024x584.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-online-orders-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-online-orders-0a-768x438.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-online-orders-0a-1536x876.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-online-orders-0a.webp 1891w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-open-home-delivery-orders" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Open Home Delivery Orders</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Inside the Online Orders section, click on <strong>Home Delivery</strong>.</li><li>A list of all home delivery orders will be displayed.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="584" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/open-home-delivery-0a-1024x584.webp" alt="Open Home Delivery" class="wp-image-11993" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/open-home-delivery-0a-1024x584.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/open-home-delivery-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/open-home-delivery-0a-768x438.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/open-home-delivery-0a-1536x876.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/open-home-delivery-0a.webp 1891w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-access-order-details" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Access Order Details</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Locate the order you want to assign.</li><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column, click the <strong>three-dot icon (â®)</strong>.</li><li>From the dropdown, select <strong>View Details</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="583" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/13-1-1024x583.webp" alt="Access Order Details" class="wp-image-9368" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/13-1-1024x583.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/13-1-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/13-1-768x437.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/13-1-1536x874.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/13-1.webp 1894w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-assign-a-delivery-man" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Assign a Delivery Man</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>On the <strong>Order Details</strong> page, scroll to the <strong>Delivery Man</strong> section (right-hand side).</li><li>Click the <strong>Assign Delivery Man</strong> button.</li><li>A modal window will open, showing all available delivery men.</li></ol><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="586" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/14-1-1024x586.webp" alt="Assign a Delivery Man" class="wp-image-9369" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/14-1-1024x586.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/14-1-300x172.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/14-1-768x440.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/14-1-1536x879.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/14-1.webp 1876w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-5-select-and-confirm" class="wp-block-heading">Step 5: Select and Confirm</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>Choose a delivery man from the list.</li><li>(Optional) Add a note in the <strong>Comments</strong> box</li><li>Click the <strong>Assign</strong> button to confirm.</li></ul><h2 id="step-6-confirmation" class="wp-block-heading">Step 6: Confirmation</h2><p>A success message will appear at the bottom-left corner of your screen, confirming that the delivery man has been successfully assigned to the order.</p><p>Following these steps ensures smooth assignment of delivery staff and timely delivery management.</p></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
                    'created_at' => '2026-02-09T09:58:18.000000Z',
