                111 => [
                    'id' => 112,
                    'doc_page_id' => 267,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => null,
                    'content_html' => '<div class="wpd6-article-content"><p>This guide will walk you through the process of editing existing employee roles and permissions. Adjusting roles ensures your team members always have the correct level of access.</p><h2 id="step-1-navigate-to-employee-role-setup" class="wp-block-heading">Step 1: Navigate to Employee Role Setup</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>From the main dashboard, open the <strong>left-hand navigation menu</strong>.</li><li>Under <strong>User Management</strong>, click on <strong>Employee &amp; Role Setup</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="584" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0a-1024x584.webp" alt="Navigate to Employee Role Setup" class="wp-image-11357" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0a-1024x584.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0a-768x438.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0a-1536x876.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0a.webp 1890w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>You will be redirected to the <strong>Employee Role List</strong> page.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="584" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0b-1024x584.webp" alt="Navigate to Employee Role Setup" class="wp-image-11359" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0b-1024x584.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0b-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0b-768x438.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0b-1536x875.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/navigate-to-employee-role-setup-0b.webp 1890w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-2-select-the-role-to-edit" class="wp-block-heading">Step 2: Select the Role to Edit</h2><ul class="wp-block-list"><li>On the Employee Role List, find the role you want to edit.</li><li>In the <strong>Action</strong> column (far right), click the <strong>three-dot menu (â®)</strong>.</li><li>From the dropdown, select <strong>Edit Role</strong>.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="579" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-the-role-to-edit-0a-1024x579.webp" alt="Select the Role to Edit" class="wp-image-11360" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-the-role-to-edit-0a-1024x579.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-the-role-to-edit-0a-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-the-role-to-edit-0a-768x434.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-the-role-to-edit-0a-1536x868.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/select-the-role-to-edit-0a.webp 1897w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-3-adjust-permissions" class="wp-block-heading">Step 3: Adjust Permissions</h2><p>On the <strong>Edit Role</strong> page, you can update the role’s modules and access levels:</p><ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>Remove Modules</strong> → Click the â next to any module to remove it from this role.</li><li><strong>Modify Module Access</strong> → For each module, set specific permissions:<ul class="wp-block-list"><li><strong>View</strong> → Allows the user to see module data.</li><li><strong>Edit</strong> → Allows the user to update information.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Mark All</strong> → Use the checkboxes to quickly enable or disable all <strong>View</strong> or <strong>Edit</strong> permissions for a module.</li></ul><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="584" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/adjust-permissions-0a-1024x584.webp" alt="Adjust Permissions" class="wp-image-11362" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/adjust-permissions-0a-1024x584.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/adjust-permissions-0a-300x171.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/adjust-permissions-0a-768x438.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/adjust-permissions-0a-1536x876.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/adjust-permissions-0a.webp 1891w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure><h2 id="step-4-save-changes" class="wp-block-heading">Step 4: Save Changes</h2><ol class="wp-block-list"><li>After making the required adjustments, click the green <strong>Update</strong> button in the top-right corner.</li><li>A success message — <strong>âRole updated successfullyâ</strong> — will appear at the bottom-left of your screen.</li><li>All employees assigned to this role will automatically inherit the updated permissions.</li></ol><p>Editing employee roles ensures your staff always have the right access to perform their duties while maintaining system security.</p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="582" src="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/editing-employee-roles-0a-1024x582.webp" alt="Editing Employee Roles" class="wp-image-11363" srcset="https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/editing-employee-roles-0a-1024x582.webp 1024w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/editing-employee-roles-0a-300x170.webp 300w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/editing-employee-roles-0a-768x436.webp 768w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/editing-employee-roles-0a-1536x872.webp 1536w, https://menumium.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/editing-employee-roles-0a.webp 1891w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></figure></div>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Cloned from version 1.0',
                    'is_snapshot' => true,
