                159 => [
                    'id' => 160,
                    'doc_page_id' => 315,
                    'user_id' => 1,
                    'content_json' => '{}',
                    'content_html' => '<p><strong>INFO</strong></p><p>As the admin panel and web app are developed using two different technologies, If you want the web app in your main domain, then you need to install the admin panel in a subdomain. For example, if you want the web app(website) in yourdomain.com, then you can install the admin panel in admin.yourdomain.com or any subdomain. Later in the web app part you will know how you need to install the web app on your server.</p><p></p><p><strong>WARNING</strong></p><p>Don’t install the admin panel or web app in a sub directory (like: yourdomain.com/folder)</p><p></p><p></p><p>6amMart requires an SSL certificate to be installed on your domain to work with all the services. A free SSL certificate can be easily installed on your domain using <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="http://sslforfree.com/">sslforfree.com</a></p><p>Let’s start the installation-</p><ul><li><p>First, hit your site URL, and it will automatically take you to the installation. Click ‘Get Started’ to start.</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-installation-page-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Installation Page SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><ul><li><p>Step 1: All the required extensions and permissions must be enabled. Check the required information if everything is OK, then click on Process Next.</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-installation-step-1-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Installation Step 01 SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><ul><li><p>Step 2: Provide your CodeCanyon username and purchase code and Continue.</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-installation-step-2-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Installation Step 02 SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><p>If you find the following page, you must activate your domain. Now fill up the information and proceed</p><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-activation-ss-1024x561.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Activation SS" width="1024" height="561" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><ul><li><p>Step 3: Now you need to set the Database host, Database name, Database username &amp; password and click Continue. If the database is in your server, then the host is localhost.</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-installation-step-3-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Installation Step 03 SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><ul><li><p>Step 4: Now, you need to import the SQL file. For this, just press Click Here to import the database.</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-installation-step-4-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Installation Step 04 SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><ul><li><p>If you find the following page, that means your database is not clean. Click ‘Force Import Database’ to import the database, which will clear your database first, then import the application’s database.</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-installation-force-import-database-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Installation Force Import Database SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><ul><li><p>Step 5: Now fill up the information and click Complete Installation</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-installation-step-5-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Installation Step 05 SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><p>Congratulations! Your software is ready to run. Click on the Admin Panel or view the Landing Page.</p><p><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/6ammart-doc-admin-installation-software-redy-to-run-page-ss-1024x531.webp" alt="6amMart Doc Admin Installation Software Ready To Run SS" width="1024" height="531" containerstyle="width: 1024px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></p><ul><li><p>Default Admin Login URL is Your-domain/<strong>login/admin</strong></p></li></ul><p>And Default Restaurant Panel Login URL is Your-domain/<strong>login/store</strong></p><p><strong>TIP</strong></p><p>Recommended tutorial is below 👇</p><h4>Share This Article :</h4><ul><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://6ammart.app/documentation/admin-application-configuration/installation/"><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/plugins/betterdocs/assets/images/social/facebook.svg?v=4.3.5" alt="Facebook" containerstyle="" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://6ammart.app/documentation/admin-application-configuration/installation/"><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/plugins/betterdocs/assets/images/social/twitter.svg?v=4.3.5" alt="X" containerstyle="" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://6ammart.app/documentation/admin-application-configuration/installation/"><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/plugins/betterdocs/assets/images/social/linkedin.svg?v=4.3.5" alt="LinkedIn" containerstyle="" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></a></p></li><li><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://6ammart.app/documentation/admin-application-configuration/installation/"><img src="https://6ammart.app/wp-content/plugins/betterdocs/assets/images/social/pinterest.svg?v=4.3.5" alt="Pinterest" containerstyle="" wrapperstyle="display: inline-block; float: left; padding-right: 8px;"></a></p></li></ul><p><a target="_blank" rel="prev" href="https://6ammart.app/documentation/admin-application-configuration/local/"> Environment Configuration</a><a target="_blank" rel="next" href="https://6ammart.app/documentation/admin-application-configuration/mandatory-setups/">Mandatory Setup</a></p>',
                    'change_summary' => 'Update',
